ng (20:20)","completed":false},{"text":"Support discussion with Ashlie and Victor on sales team usage of campaign fields and attribution tracking (17:14)","completed":false},{"text":"Monitor SharePoint folder creation and access by Victor; ensure team coordination (07:21)","completed":false},{"text":"Ensure project plan access to Betty and Lewis and coordinate team reference (28:42)","completed":false},{"text":"Follow up on access and email sharing issues with SharePoint (21:09)","completed":false}]'::jsonb,
