 just.","index":349,"end_time":1329.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1328.79,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"And then I think it was just replacing this with a testimonial.","index":350,"end_time":1333.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1329.83,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Now we just put the company name because that guy, he''s from Workhouse, I think.","index":351,"end_time":1337.13,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1334.29,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"I think it always looks more legit if you put the name of the company and not the person.","index":352,"end_time":1343.25,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1337.13,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Because this is the other project manager.","index":353,"end_time":1344.69,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1343.25,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"That could be anyone.","index":354,"end_time":1346.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1344.69,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Right.","index":355,"end_time":1347.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1346.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think it is.","index":356,"end_time":1347.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1347.05,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Just has more.","index":357,"end_time":1348.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1347.65,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"It''s more convincing if you have real.","index":358,"end_time":1351.17,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1349.41,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Company name there, you know.","index":359,"end_time":1352.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1351.17,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Okay, this is the client.","index":360,"end_time":1353.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1352.33,"speaker_name":"Axel Völker"},{"text":"Yep.","index":361,"end_time":1354.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1353.73,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No, actually, do you think it makes sense to use someone from the companies which logos are just above?","index":362,"end_time":1361.25,"speaker_id":1,"st