:"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"So are you including things like that in your audit or is it only purely a HubSpot audit?","index":241,"end_time":624.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":619.32,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"What is your.","index":242,"end_time":625.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":624.88,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":243,"end_time":626.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":625.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The scope of the audit was more to clean up just years and years of like data that had been layered on top of each other.","index":244,"end_time":631.96,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":626.28,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":245,"end_time":632.58,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":632.26,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"And you can ask Josh.","index":246,"end_time":634.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":633.46,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, I told them from day one of meeting, like, guys, this, this is not as clean and operational as I would like it to be.","index":247,"end_time":641.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":634.38,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The HubSpot.","index":248,"end_time":643.38,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":642.5,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Yeah, the HubSpot.","index":249,"end_time":644.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":643.62,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":250,"end_time":644.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":644.5,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"I mean just duplicate of properties, missing information.","index":251,"end_time":648.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":645.46,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":252,"end_time":650.5,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":650.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"In the audit I point out that 95% of properties are not even being filled in.","index":253,"end_time":656.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":650.5,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So there''s just a huge waste.","index":254,"end_time":657.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":656.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"What about the lead management process?","index":255,"end_time":659.46,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":657.78,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Because I, I, by the way, I haven''t even had a deep dive with Josh, so I''ve got a list of question him.","index":256,"end_time":664.48,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":659.46,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"So if I''m asking you things that I should just ask him, feel free.","index":257,"end_time":668.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":665.36,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"But that''s the other thing that stood out for me, is for me there''s no connection from the front end campaigns leads to that qualified, you know, opportunity kind of thing.","index":258,"end_time":682.12,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":668.96,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"So yeah, are you guys doing that or are you just really strictly focusing on campaigns at this point?","index":259,"end_time":687.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":682.12,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"So what PTO Exchange strives for in all marketing is to get a first meeting booked for sales, which I''m sure.","index":260,"end_time":695.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":687.68,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I understand that, but are you like, are you, are you leading the lead management or is that not part of your like, what is your, what do you call the word?","index":261,"end_time":710.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":695.64,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Like you, what you guys do, you''re, you know, like, what''s your.","index":262,"end_time":713.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":710.36,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"What''s like, do you have in that portal that you''re going to give me?","index":263,"end_time":717.36,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":713.96,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Client portal.","index":264,"end_time":718.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":717.36,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"What exactly your role is, what you guys are tasked to do, what are you tasked to deliver?","index":265,"end_time":723,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":718.2,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Is that list anywhere?","index":266,"end_time":724.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":723.16,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"I mean, it would be in our scope of work, like contract.","index":267,"end_time":728.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":725.77,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":268,"end_time":729.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":728.65,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, let me look at.","index":269,"end_time":729.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":729.01,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"And that''s there, right?","index":270,"end_time":730.45,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":729.81,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"And that''s impulse as well.","index":271,"end_time":731.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":730.45,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":272,"end_time":731.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":731.49,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Client portal.","index":273,"end_time":732.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":731.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Are you trying to get more like, at what point do you pitch?","index":274,"end_time":737.21,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":733.05,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"So you pitched in April, you got the work, but.","index":275,"end_time":739.53,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":737.21,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"And this is just an audit of HubSpot, so that''s not going to be like Are you at some point going to pitch for more stuff or do you just kind of do it?","index":276,"end_time":746.93,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":739.77,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"I mean.","index":277,"end_time":747.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":746.93,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Oh, like last week we pitched four new campaign ideas and Josh approved all of them.","index":278,"end_time":751.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":747.37,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And so we''re like, in the midst of developing landing pages and email content and all sorts of stuff for those now.","index":279,"end_time":755.72,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":751.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, so that.","index":280,"end_time":756.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":756.19,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"That''s a little bit down here versus being more strategy, but so which is fine because that''s kind of why I''m coming in to try to help strategy.","index":281,"end_time":763.27,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":756.91,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"But.","index":282,"end_time":763.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":763.27,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"But are those, though, industry campaigns?","index":283,"end_time":766.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":764.35,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Yes, industry focus camps.","index":284,"end_time":768.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":766.75,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"So prior to that, they weren''t doing industry campaigns or were they you just trying to improve things?","index":285,"end_time":772.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":768.47,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"I mean, we''re always trying to improve our metrics.","index":286,"end_time":774.51,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":772.67,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We were very focused on healthcare and HR personnel, and we want to expand because now we have more, you know, once the website pages are approved, we have more content that we can send to them and get them to browse the site more.","index":287,"end_time":785.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":774.51,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And, and so, and so the, the land, the new web pages that you''re doing for industries.","index":288,"end_time":792.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":786,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Right.","index":289,"end_time":792.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":792.4,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Are they published yet or are they going to be published?","index":290,"end_time":795.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":793.44,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"No, they''re.","index":291,"end_time":796.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":795.68,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"They''re sitting in Josh''s review plate right now.","index":292,"end_time":798.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":796.2,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But aren''t.","index":293,"end_time":799.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":798.64,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Wouldn''t the campaigns.","index":294,"end_time":800.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":799.28,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"But the campaigns are not going to the web pages.","index":295,"end_time":802.24,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":800.32,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"The campaigns are going to land those.","index":296,"end_time":803.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":802.24,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Those new campaigns are not live.","index":297,"end_time":805.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":803.84,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Those would be the pages I would send them to.","index":298,"end_time":807.64,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":805.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":299,"end_time":808.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":807.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":300,"end_time":808.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":808.16,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Got it, Got it.","index":301,"end_time":809.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":808.68,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":302,"end_time":809.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":809.32,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Okay.","index":303,"end_time":810.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":810.32,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"And are you also doing the lead magnets?","index":304,"end_time":814.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":811.68,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":305,"end_time":814.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":814.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Like LinkedIn lead generation.","index":306,"end_time":816.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":814.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":307,"end_time":816.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":816.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Or are you talking more from a content perspective?","index":308,"end_time":819.75,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":817.75,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yes.","index":309,"end_time":820.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":819.75,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":310,"end_time":820.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":820.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we''re working for those campaigns.","index":311,"end_time":822.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":820.67,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Part of them are developing infographics or playbooks as magnets.","index":312,"end_time":826.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":822.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And that''s all part of.","index":313,"end_time":828.47,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":826.87,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"As in I should be able to find that.","index":314,"end_time":830.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":828.47,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Right.","index":315,"end_time":830.509,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":830.15,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"So when I go, Are you going to present it today?","index":316,"end_time":832.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":830.509,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"No, not today.","index":317,"end_time":833.91,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":833.11,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We just got it approved last week.","index":318,"end_time":835.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":833.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we''re in the midst of writing and designing all of these.","index":319,"end_time":837.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":835.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, so let me go find your proposal.","index":320,"end_time":841.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":838.31,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Our scope of work.","index":321,"end_time":843.52,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":842.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, well.","index":322,"end_time":844.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":843.84,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Oh, so, okay, so what you.","index":323,"end_time":846.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":844.8,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Or do you want, like, the document outlining, like, the four campaigns?","index":324,"end_time":849.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":846.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, if I can find it all in there, great.","index":325,"end_time":851.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":849.28,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"But if there, if you can help make sure I find all this, because I want to get up to speed so that I can, you know, obviously understand what we''re trying to do.","index":326,"end_time":861.28,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":851.6,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Right.","index":327,"end_time":862.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":862.16,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"I mean, I call and I believe.","index":328,"end_time":866.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":863.76,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"I believe the goal is for me to take over and drive and direct this stuff off of Josh''s plate, I think.","index":329,"end_time":872.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":867.15,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":330,"end_time":873.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":872.83,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And that''s my execution arm.","index":331,"end_time":875.71,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":873.55,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":332,"end_time":876.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":875.87,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":333,"end_time":876.71,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":876.23,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"I just want to make sure that was.","index":334,"end_time":878.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":876.71,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"That''s my understanding too.","index":335,"end_time":879.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":878.11,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Okay, cool.","index":336,"end_time":879.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":879.31,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"So I just want to really understand what''s going on.","index":337,"end_time":882.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":880.11,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"So.","index":338,"end_time":882.67,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":882.31,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":339,"end_time":882.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":882.67,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And if you want to come in and you want to like scrap whatever.","index":340,"end_time":885.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":882.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Let''s stand this up.","index":341,"end_time":886.79,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":885.63,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Xyz.","index":342,"end_time":887.47,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":886.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean we will build like our understanding is we''re partners in this.","index":343,"end_time":890.55,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":887.47,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We want to just help.","index":344,"end_time":891.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":890.55,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":345,"end_time":892.55,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":892.11,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Drive the bottom line for PTO exchange.","index":346,"end_time":894.27,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":892.55,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And I''ll be honest with you, I don''t know enough yet.","index":347,"end_time":896.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":894.27,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Right.","index":348,"end_time":896.51,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":896.15,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"So.","index":349,"end_time":896.91,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":896.51,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"And I have to do my it.","index":350,"end_time":899.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":897.23,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"And just to give you a perspective, where I''m coming from is where I really want to focus on is understanding their business, understanding their Personas, the competition of market and how what their unique proposition.","index":351,"end_time":912.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":899.09,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Right.","index":352,"end_time":913.13,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":912.81,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Their unique positioning is.","index":353,"end_time":914.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":913.13,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"So that''s the work I want to do.","index":354,"end_time":916.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":914.41,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"And when we have alignment and agreement there, then I want to.","index":355,"end_time":920.81,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":916.81,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"And some of the stuff you guys are doing is, is perfect because honestly it''s kind of the early stuff.","index":356,"end_time":926.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":920.81,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"And then I, I want to help work with you on going