 Williams"},{"text":"And that''s where I think some outbound a different shifting internally here and then working with you too.","index":395,"end_time":1034.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1026.48,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"So.","index":396,"end_time":1035.16,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1034.92,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Okay.","index":397,"end_time":1035.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1035.16,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"There was one other thing I was going to say.","index":398,"end_time":1039.4,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1037.72,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Oh.","index":399,"end_time":1039.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1039.4,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"This really struck me.","index":400,"end_time":1041.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1040.36,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"I''m curious if it struck you guys.","index":401,"end_time":1043.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1041.8,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"238,000 contact records, so leads universe.","index":402,"end_time":1053.639,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1045.24,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"I didn''t see a lot of organization at this point.","index":403,"end_time":1057.079,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1054.919,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"So I trust.","index":404,"end_time":1057.679,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1057.079,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"I''m suspecting your audit''s going to talk to that understanding that database.","index":405,"end_time":1062.679,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1057.679,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Right.","index":406,"end_time":1063.159,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1062.759,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"And, and doing the analysis to segment and, and work it.","index":407,"end_time":1067.119,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1063.319,"speaker_name":"Carmen Williams"},{"text":"Right, right.","index":408,"end_time":1068.599,"spe