-- Meeting: Aligned Growth Engine | Kickoff (2026-01-22 16:30:00+00)
WITH new_meeting AS (
  INSERT INTO compass_meetings (contract_id, meeting_date, source, external_id, title, participants, duration_seconds, recording_url, transcript, sentiment, raw_metadata, created_at, updated_at)
  VALUES (
    'fc929bc1-8e6d-4718-8058-6510ab343d75',
    '2026-01-22 16:30:00+00',
    'fireflies',
    '01KFECHXBBKV6KA36PZCK3CDCT',
    'Aligned Growth Engine | Kickoff',
    '{"Douglas SMith","Justin Brown","Colin Costigan","Douglas SMith","Douglas SMith","Kerry Marker"}'::text[],
    3581,
    'https://us02web.zoom.us/j/86149189126?pwd=DaHy4wIGxB0N93hUPm3AQFZhYuA2gP.1&jst=2',
    '{"id":"01KFECHXBBKV6KA36PZCK3CDCT","title":"Aligned Growth Engine | Kickoff","summary":{"notes":"## **Target Market Definition**\n\nThe team agreed to focus on **target organizations between $1 billion and $50 billion in revenue**, prioritizing verticals like manufacturing, retail, consumer packaged goods, healthcare, fintech, and excluding government clients (10:14).  \n- **Douglas Smith** emphasized tailoring lower-revenue targets (sub-$1 billion) when part of larger portfolios such as private equity holdings.  \n- The ideal contacts are **CIOs, CTOs, CISOs, and their direct reports**, with an emphasis on new or recently expanded roles as key triggers for engagement.  \n- Market complexity and deal velocity vary by vertical, with healthcare providers and manufacturing having slower sales cycles due to procurement and organizational factors (18:30).  \n- Expansion within existing clients is secondary; the primary goal is **net new client acquisition** and building broader market awareness (22:04).\n\n## **Lead Generation and Signal Capture Strategy**\n\nThe firm currently lacks automated methods to capture real-time signals such as new leadership hires or modernization efforts, relying on manual LinkedIn Sales Navigator searches without export capabilities (16:21).  \n- **Colin Costigan** noted their own use of account-based marketing tools capable of detecting signals like new job hires within customizable timeframes (3, 6, 12 months) to automate campaign targeting (17:42).  \n- Multiple segmented campaigns will be required to address diverse pain points and growth priorities across different buyer personas, supporting differentiated messaging (30:08).  \n- Procurement delays of **weeks to months** affect deal timelines, necessitating a realistic sales cycle approach (21:31).\n\n## **First Hundred Days Offering and Strategic Differentiation**\n\nAcacia’s **First Hundred Days service** targets new technical leaders to help them make informed decisions quickly while avoiding costly missteps, a critical window that shapes their long-term success (35:41).  \n- The approach is grounded in research and refined with organizational psychology expertise to address typical leadership challenges beyond technology alone (43:24).  \n- The offering delivers a **year-one narrative and roadmap within six weeks**, compressible to 4-5 weeks using diagnostic tools and AI-enhanced stakeholder interviews (41:23).  \n- Differentiation relies on high-quality analysis, leadership transition support, and tailored advice, positioning Acacia against competitors like Deloitte Labs by focusing on actionable insights rather than generic consulting (43:50).  \n- **Douglas Smith** highlighted the short average tenure of CIOs (~2 years), underscoring the need for rapid, thoughtful onboarding and decision-making support (44:41).\n\n## **AI and Data Strategy in Market Positioning**\n\nAI is positioned as an embedded capability within broader strategies, not as a standalone offering, reflecting varied client maturity and needs (15:36).  \n- **Douglas Smith** shared examples ranging from highly advanced pharma clients investing billions in AI with limited advisory opportunity but strong product potential, to manufacturers constrained by budgets and entrenched operations, indicating different engagement models (24:10).  \n- The middle market segment shows fragmented AI adoption with boards pressuring for clearer value and cohesion, providing a potential advisory entry point (27:34).  \n- Messaging will need to be segmented to resonate with CIOs focused on cost pressures and efficiency gains, recognizing that CIOs are often not the primary AI adoption leaders in their organizations (27:34).\n\n## **Content Creation and Marketing Collaboration**\n\nThe leadership team expressed strong willingness to engage in content creation, seeing it as a powerful tool to build credibility and connect with target audiences (45:05).  \n- **Douglas Smith** is actively using AI tools like Claude and ChatGPT to organize and repurpose thousands of documents into marketable frameworks and go-to-market materials (46:31).  \n- The team is open to experimenting with various content formats including video series, Loom videos, and conversational AI demos to tell stories and showcase expertise (48:21).  \n- This content-driven approach is expected to differentiate Acacia in a crowded market by highlighting authentic insights from practitioners rather than generic marketing messaging (49:26).\n\n## **Next Steps and Infrastructure Alignment**\n\nThe next meeting will focus on alignment and roadmap delivery after Acacia shares key documents and provides CRM access for data verification (57:06).  \n- The team uses **Pipedrive** for CRM management and will respond asynchronously to infrastructure and tool-related questions before the next call (58:12).  \n- Colin Costigan described their process of combining competitive research and internal data to build a detailed roadmap with annual goals and quarterly tasks, ensuring actionable marketing and sales alignment (56:50).  \n- The collaborative approach, with Acacia’s detailed input, is expected to accelerate lead generation and go-to-market effectiveness.","outline":null,"keywords":["Acacia","CIO transitions","Lead generation","AI readiness","Go-to-market strategy","Account-based marketing"],"overview":"- **Target Market Focus:** Prioritize organizations with $1-50 billion revenue; sectors include manufacturing, retail, and healthcare.  \n- **Lead Generation Gaps:** Currently manual signal capture; need automation to track leadership changes and market signals efficiently.  \n- **First Hundred Days Service:** Supports new leaders with fast, informed decisions; offers roadmap within 4-6 weeks using advanced tools.  \n- **AI Strategy Overview:** AI integrated into broader strategies; middle market faces varied adoption rates, needing tailored advisory approaches.  \n- **Content Creation Plans:** Team eager to leverage content for credibility; experimenting with diverse formats to share authentic insights.  \n- **Next Steps:** Upcoming meeting to align on roadmap after sharing key documents; focus on enhancing CRM data verification.","action_items":"\n**Douglas Smith**\nShare the pitch deck for Acacia, and the “First 100 Days” offering materials in markdown and slide formats (32:52)\nProvide the documented output of go-to-market conversations, including strategy, differentiation, offerings, and competitor analysis (51:17)\nShare access or links to the Manus knowledge base site with marketing and strategy frameworks (52:47)\n\n**Colin Costigan**\nFollow up by email requesting the above documents from Doug and include the whole team (58:47)\nSend marketing infrastructure questions to Kerry for asynchronous response (52:58)\nSchedule the next alignment meeting via availability link for Carrie to review calendars (58:20)\n\n**Kerry Marker**\nReview and respond to marketing infrastructure questions asynchronously (52:58)\nCoordinate calendar availability and confirm the next meeting date with Colin (58:21)\nPossibly assist in collating output from previous go-to-market discussions for sharing (51:42)\n\n**Justin Brown**\nEngage in creating marketing content and help coordinate conversation around content creation initiatives (45:05)\n"},"duration":59.68000030517578,"speakers":[{"id":0,"name":"Douglas SMith"},{"id":1,"name":"Justin Brown"},{"id":2,"name":"Colin Costigan"},{"id":3,"name":"Douglas SMith"},{"id":4,"name":"Douglas SMith"},{"id":5,"name":"Kerry Marker"}],"sentences":[{"text":"Hey, how''s it going?","index":0,"end_time":13.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":12.08,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"We match.","index":1,"end_time":15.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":14.56,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"We do.","index":2,"end_time":17.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":16.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And I decided on the first call.","index":3,"end_time":18.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":17.12,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And people also think we''re related, so.","index":4,"end_time":20.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":18.8,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"This is.","index":5,"end_time":21.36,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":20.84,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Super funny.","index":6,"end_time":24.16,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":23.2,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I can see it.","index":7,"end_time":28.89,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":28.17,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I got a. I got reddish.","index":8,"end_time":30.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":29.37,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Reddish tint.","index":9,"end_time":31.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":30.69,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"I got a red.","index":10,"end_time":32.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":31.49,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Red beard in the sun.","index":11,"end_time":33.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":32.13,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Much more red than probably looks on camera.","index":12,"end_time":37.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":33.69,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"And I had.","index":13,"end_time":43.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":42.57,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"I had basically your color hair when I was little.","index":14,"end_time":48.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":43.77,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Oh, really?","index":15,"end_time":49.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":48.73,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I had red hair.","index":16,"end_time":51.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":50.09,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Probably more like auburn.","index":17,"end_time":52.77,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":51.13,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Like, a little darker, but, like, still definitely red darkened.","index":18,"end_time":58.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":52.77,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"I think it''s really, like blonde in the summer.","index":19,"end_time":61.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":59.09,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":20,"end_time":62.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":61.65,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":21,"end_time":67.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":67.09,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''ll see what color my daughter''s hair is.","index":22,"end_time":69.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":67.41,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"It''s like very, like, strawberry right now.","index":23,"end_time":71.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":69.33,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":24,"end_time":74.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":73.57,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Mine, like, it''s.","index":25,"end_time":74.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":74.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"She''s been different hair color every day.","index":26,"end_time":76.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":74.97,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I swear.","index":27,"end_time":77.45,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":76.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"She''s like blonde someday and then brown and then has some red.","index":28,"end_time":80.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":77.45,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No.","index":29,"end_time":86.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":86.86,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Carrie mentioned that they had several meetings going on, so.","index":30,"end_time":91.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":86.98,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay.","index":31,"end_time":92.14,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":91.58,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Fits.","index":32,"end_time":92.78,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":92.22,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":33,"end_time":93.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":93.18,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Seemed like maybe you guys had some zoom issues the first couple of meetings.","index":34,"end_time":98.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":95.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":35,"end_time":99.82,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":99.26,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":36,"end_time":100.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":100.62,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"I don''t know what was going on.","index":37,"end_time":102.38,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":100.94,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":38,"end_time":107.34,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":107.02,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I don''t.","index":39,"end_time":107.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":107.34,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I don''t have any idea.","index":40,"end_time":109.02,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":107.74,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"It worked.","index":41,"end_time":110.8,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":110.36,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"My meeting before and after, so.","index":42,"end_time":112.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":110.8,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":43,"end_time":113.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":112.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"There she is.","index":44,"end_time":153.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":152.53,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Good morning.","index":45,"end_time":160.94,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":160.46,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Hey.","index":46,"end_time":162.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":161.66,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"How''s everyone doing?","index":47,"end_time":164.86,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":163.74,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Good.","index":48,"end_time":166.06,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":165.66,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"How are you?","index":49,"end_time":167.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":166.94,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Doing well.","index":50,"end_time":168.86,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":168.14,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Doing well.","index":51,"end_time":169.9,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":169.1,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"What were you go.","index":52,"end_time":171.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":170.46,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"I mean, you can go to the national championship for any reason, but I was looking at your LinkedIn, your Penn State.","index":53,"end_time":176.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":171.34,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"What was your.","index":54,"end_time":177.98,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":177.26,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Like, do you just go to the national championship?","index":55,"end_time":180.74,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":177.98,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Is like significant other.","index":56,"end_time":182.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":180.74,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"No.","index":57,"end_time":183.82,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":183.42,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"So.","index":58,"end_time":184.22,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":183.82,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"So I''m Penn State.","index":59,"end_time":185.42,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":184.46,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"My dad actually went to Miami.","index":60,"end_time":187.26,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":185.5,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Okay.","index":61,"end_time":188.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":187.5,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Half of college, so I always grew up a Miami fan, but one of my best friends, her son is a current student at Miami.","index":62,"end_time":195.26,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":188.38,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Okay.","index":63,"end_time":196.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":195.58,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"So he was begging her to come down, so she asked me to.","index":64,"end_time":199.58,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":196.1,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"To come with her, so.","index":65,"end_time":201.22,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":199.9,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":66,"end_time":201.7,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":201.22,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"It was a great game.","index":67,"end_time":202.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":201.7,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"I''m sorry Miami didn''t win, but, yeah, you get to see a fun one.","index":68,"end_time":206.34,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":202.54,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"It hasn''t been that way.","index":69,"end_time":207.62,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":206.34,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"The.","index":70,"end_time":207.98,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":207.62,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"The last, like, five national championships have been blowouts.","index":71,"end_time":210.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":207.98,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Blowouts.","index":72,"end_time":211.38,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":210.82,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"I know.","index":73,"end_time":211.74,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":211.38,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"And I honestly thought it would be an Indiana blowout.","index":74,"end_time":214.26,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":211.74,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"So her son, you know, he had a ticket to the game and that kind of thing, so I''m just glad he caught a good game, you know?","index":75,"end_time":220.61,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":214.26,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":76,"end_time":220.93,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":220.61,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":77,"end_time":221.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":220.93,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Miami kept fighting back.","index":78,"end_time":222.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":221.25,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"They did quite terribly in the first half because then it would have been.","index":79,"end_time":227.57,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":222.69,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Would have been a swing in the other direction.","index":80,"end_time":230.45,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":227.89,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":81,"end_time":231.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":230.93,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"I''d like to introduce Colin.","index":82,"end_time":233.41,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":231.49,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"We realized that we matched today, so it was not coordinated, but maybe we''re just on the same page.","index":83,"end_time":240.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":233.65,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"But Colin is our head of client operations.","index":84,"end_time":244.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":240.89,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"He''s going to be leading us through a lot of the engagement over the next couple of weeks.","index":85,"end_time":250.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":244.45,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"And yeah, Colin, I don''t know, kind of just introduced you for you, but.","index":86,"end_time":255.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":251.25,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Happy to do the intro on our side too.","index":87,"end_time":259.45,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":257.33,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"So Doug Smith will be joining any second.","index":88,"end_time":261.41,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":259.45,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"He and I just wrapped another call that ran a few minutes over.","index":89,"end_time":264.53,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":261.41,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"So sorry we were a minute late, but Doug and I are the co founders of the firm, so I thought it would be beneficial that he and I are both on the conversation.","index":90,"end_time":272.21,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":264.53,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"And then I also wanted to loop in Cyrus.","index":91,"end_time":274.77,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":272.85,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"So Cyrus has been with Acacia now probably a year, I would guess Cyrus.","index":92,"end_time":280.03,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":274.77,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"And he is sort of all things.","index":93,"end_time":282.51,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":280.91,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"So he has done consulting for us on clients, but he''s also a bit of a tech guru that has been helping us with some website and branding and integrations and those types of things.","index":94,"end_time":294.59,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":282.67,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"So thought it would be beneficial for him to be here as well, because I''m sure some of the questions that you have, he''ll probably be better to answer than I would be.","index":95,"end_time":302.99,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":294.67,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"So in an effort to try and really steam, you know, streamline the whole process, just wanted to bring him to the call too.","index":96,"end_time":310.91,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":303.15,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":97,"end_time":311.79,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":311.23,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"That''s great, Tyrus.","index":98,"end_time":313.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":311.79,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Great to meet you.","index":99,"end_time":314.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":313.31,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Yeah, to meet you too.","index":100,"end_time":315.39,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":314.35,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Happy to support in any way I can.","index":101,"end_time":316.99,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":315.39,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":102,"end_time":318.03,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":317.47,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Well, with that, Carrie, do you want us to jump in or you want us to wait for Doug?","index":103,"end_time":321.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":318.27,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"You can go ahead and.","index":104,"end_time":322.83,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":321.87,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"And jump in just because I know we have some time constraints and then we can get him up to speed.","index":105,"end_time":327.95,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":322.83,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"All right, sounds.","index":106,"end_time":329.11,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":328.27,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Sounds great.","index":107,"end_time":329.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":329.11,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":108,"end_time":330.99,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":330.67,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So before we dive into, you know, tactics, channels, all of the, like in the weeds conversations, we need to know, have these series of conversations and I know Justin walked you through, you know, what our land growth engine looks like.","index":109,"end_time":342.3,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":330.99,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I watched those calls.","index":110,"end_time":343.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":342.3,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So, Carrie, I feel like I know you a little bit and I''m excited for us to get to know each other, but, you know, everything that you shared in the intake form that you filled out this morning, thank you for that, by the way.","index":111,"end_time":351.7,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":343.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And just those earlier conversations, it''s not doing marketing for marketing sake, right?","index":112,"end_time":356.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":351.7,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Like, we need marketing to drive actual results.","index":113,"end_time":358.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":356.58,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"There''s going to be some things along the way that don''t feel like they''re immediately driving results.","index":114,"end_time":362.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":358.98,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Like, hey, guys, we do need to build a new landing page or we need to update X, Y and Z.","index":115,"end_time":366.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":362.86,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s not going to be like, cool.","index":116,"end_time":368.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":367.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Soon as we launch that landing page, 100 new leads came in.","index":117,"end_time":371.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":368.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But we need to have all of the pieces in place to.","index":118,"end_time":375.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":372.19,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"To be able to build a strong marketing campaign and marketing funnel that operates.","index":119,"end_time":379.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":375.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And we look at it like an engine.","index":120,"end_time":381.43,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":379.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It should be able to Operate on its own, where we are really ingrained in it.","index":121,"end_time":387.27,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":381.43,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You know, we''re working and turning the cogs of it, but we''re also, you know, determining what are we exactly putting into it.","index":122,"end_time":391.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":387.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Does a new machine need to be added into, into the tech stack?","index":123,"end_time":395.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":391.75,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You know, how are we going to automate this process so that Carrie and Doug and Cyrus are living their best life and marketing is delivering high quality leads.","index":124,"end_time":404.14,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":395.22,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So like I said, there''s a lot of things along the way that don''t feel like they drive leads directly.","index":125,"end_time":408.62,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":404.46,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But we need to have these conversations up front, pour concrete into the foundation, and then we start to build the framework of the house.","index":126,"end_time":414.46,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":408.62,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Does all that make sense?","index":127,"end_time":416.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":415.18,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, absolutely.","index":128,"end_time":417.26,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":416.22,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":129,"end_time":417.98,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":417.42,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And there''s a few things that I want to.","index":130,"end_time":419.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":418.46,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I always like to start these conversations with just aligning because I wasn''t in those first conversations.","index":131,"end_time":424.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":419.9,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I always want to make sure that I''m reading everything correctly.","index":132,"end_time":427.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":424.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we want Acacia to feel like a high end technology advisory, not the run of the mill general consulting firm.","index":133,"end_time":435.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":427.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"When a CIO or a CTO is checking out your website or checking out your LinkedIn, they should immediately have some sort of understanding of who you are, what you do, and why you''re different than competitors, why they should roll with you.","index":134,"end_time":448.05,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":436.77,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Lead generation is a top priority and everything else is going to operate in service of that.","index":135,"end_time":453.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":448.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And historically, from what I''ve heard, you guys have grown mainly through relationships and some cold outreach, but it hasn''t really been a scalable approach.","index":136,"end_time":460.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":453.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Is any of that offer is all that accurate?","index":137,"end_time":462.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":460.57,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No, that is, that is correct.","index":138,"end_time":465.09,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":463.13,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"It''s been pretty much just growth through relationships, former clients, relationships that people have in network, former consultants of ours, et cetera.","index":139,"end_time":475.29,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":465.09,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"And we''ve kind of relied on that.","index":140,"end_time":477.85,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":475.61,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"But now we''re sort of at that inflection point starting year three, year four here, that, that isn''t sustainable, especially for the level of growth that we''re looking for.","index":141,"end_time":487.08,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":477.85,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Gotcha.","index":142,"end_time":487.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":487.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And if I remember correctly, you have a background in marketing and Doug has a background as a CIO or CTO as well, correct?","index":143,"end_time":494.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":487.96,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yes.","index":144,"end_time":495.36,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":494.96,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"So Doug is former cio.","index":145,"end_time":497.32,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":495.36,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"I started my career in marketing primarily in field marketing.","index":146,"end_time":501.88,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":498.28,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"So a lot of it was, you know, campaigns and events driven, supporting specific regions, but primarily in.","index":147,"end_time":507.72,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":501.88,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"In only technology organizations like SAP and Apptio and Qlik and others.","index":148,"end_time":512.83,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":508.67,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":149,"end_time":513.79,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":513.23,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Well, got the makings for a great relationship here.","index":150,"end_time":516.35,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":513.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":151,"end_time":518.59,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":517.95,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"All right, well, I''m going to pull up my screen.","index":152,"end_time":520.19,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":518.59,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"To be completely candid with you guys, I do not like to have a slide deck up on the screen.","index":153,"end_time":525.87,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":520.67,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"The whole time.","index":154,"end_time":526.39,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":525.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''re going to be talking for an hour today and I''ll give you a preview.","index":155,"end_time":529.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":526.39,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Our agenda is going to dive into ideal customers, understanding your guys solution you''re offering the market and you know, your main competitors that you guys are seeing every day, how you differentiate yourselves, any marketing infrastructure you currently have in place and then really aligning on those strategic priorities to give you a snapshot of what these look like.","index":156,"end_time":549.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":530.11,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s a lot of questions that I''m going to be asking you.","index":157,"end_time":550.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":549.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I don''t want to have this unattractive thing up on the page.","index":158,"end_time":553.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":550.8,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I like to have a very organic conversation.","index":159,"end_time":555.12,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":553.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"But again to be completely transparent, this first meeting is going to be a lot of you talking and me really absorbing so that I can work with the information at hand.","index":160,"end_time":564.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":555.84,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then when we leave this meeting it would be great maybe if we could get access to your CRM or just some pool of data so that we can verify some numbers and some metrics to what we''re seeing out in the market.","index":161,"end_time":574.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":564.37,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So if that sounds like a plan, I''m going to get started with focus on the ideal customers.","index":162,"end_time":579.01,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":574.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, that sounds great.","index":163,"end_time":580.21,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":579.17,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"And Doug is here by the way.","index":164,"end_time":581.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":580.29,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Hello, Doug.","index":165,"end_time":582.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":581.69,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Hey Doug.","index":166,"end_time":583.09,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":582.41,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Hey everybody.","index":167,"end_time":585.49,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":584.61,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Thank you.","index":168,"end_time":586.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":585.73,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Great to meet you.","index":169,"end_time":588.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":587.81,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Nice to meet you both.","index":170,"end_time":590.68,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":589.8,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Doug.","index":171,"end_time":591.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":591.16,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Doug Smith with a capital M. Yeah.","index":172,"end_time":594.32,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":591.56,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"That''S my, that''s right.","index":173,"end_time":595.88,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":594.32,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"That''s got to be fixed.","index":174,"end_time":597.48,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":595.88,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Call it.","index":175,"end_time":600.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":599.32,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"That''s Doug.","index":176,"end_time":602.84,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":601.96,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"All right, well Doug, it''s great, great to meet you.","index":177,"end_time":606.2,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":603.48,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Thanks for jumping on this morning And Colin with that, I will let you take it away because I know you have a zillion questions, which is great.","index":178,"end_time":613.88,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":606.2,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":179,"end_time":615,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":614.52,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So you know, based on kind of what we''ve even talked about already in today''s meeting and what you shared with Justin, so CIOs, CTOs, CISOs, maybe their direct reports starting from conversations with them as well, roughly like a 500,000 to 5 billion revenue range, kind of a large like anyone falls within this and then multiple industries.","index":180,"end_time":635.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":616.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Hold on.","index":181,"end_time":637.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":636.51,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Yeah, I think, I think I''m going to adjust that up so I think you know, up to.","index":182,"end_time":644.2,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":637.11,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Depending on the vertical, up to let''s say 20 billion in revenue.","index":183,"end_time":653.72,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":647,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And I''d like to sort of cut.","index":184,"end_time":657.32,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":655.4,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Off the bottom a little bit too well.","index":185,"end_time":660.28,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":657.32,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean Doug, my, my perspective was and I had shared with them like we''ve worked with 10 billion dollar organizations.","index":186,"end_time":666.2,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":660.28,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Obviously they''re ripe for, you know, transformation work etc, but like the Fortune 50s of the world are probably already working with Deloitte McKinsey, KPMG and others and if we were going to get someone to actually respond and take the meeting who probably has more stuff going on, they''re probably on the lower, like the lower end.","index":187,"end_time":687.22,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":666.28,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"So I said from like a primary target perspective and the people that probably would be most likely and or quickest to buy are going to fall in that range.","index":188,"end_time":695.38,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":687.22,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"But we''re certainly, you know certainly open to targeting and going after larger organizations especially if they fall in manufacturing, retail, see apg, you know, healthcare, fintech etc.","index":189,"end_time":708.24,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":695.78,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Yeah, that works.","index":190,"end_time":711.92,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":709.36,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So.","index":191,"end_time":713.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":713.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think.","index":192,"end_time":717.44,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":716.88,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"We can get you very like we can get you very.","index":193,"end_time":722.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":719.2,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Specific sort of targets if you will Colin and Justin.","index":194,"end_time":728.08,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":722.12,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"But yeah, somewhere between I, I think.","index":195,"end_time":733.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":729.28,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"It does as Carrie pointed it out.","index":196,"end_time":735.11,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":733.15,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Really matter about the vertical and it also you know we''re, I, I have conversations with and I''ll give you an.","index":197,"end_time":745.79,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":735.11,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Example with a 300 billion dollar company.","index":198,"end_time":747.91,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":745.79,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"That you know they took the, they took the call.","index":199,"end_time":752.23,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":748.63,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"It''s going to take a year to.","index":200,"end_time":753.75,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":752.55,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Close them but they took the call.","index":201,"end_time":755.11,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":753.75,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Understand the value proposition but those are.","index":202,"end_time":759.54,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":755.91,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Rare for them to take that call.","index":203,"end_time":761.58,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":759.54,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right.","index":204,"end_time":762.06,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":761.66,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Or massive, massive.","index":205,"end_time":765.18,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":762.06,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"But they saw my background and specific to their vertical and said okay, I''ll take the call.","index":206,"end_time":771.5,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":765.18,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I think you know multi site, multi business unit, multi region operations is important.","index":207,"end_time":780.7,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":773.82,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right.","index":208,"end_time":781.82,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":781.42,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And not government.","index":209,"end_time":786.07,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":784.71,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"The exclusions.","index":210,"end_time":788.27,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":787.43,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"What it''s not.","index":211,"end_time":789.11,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":788.27,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I think healthcare provider payer life sciences to some degree manufacturing, industrials, financial services.","index":212,"end_time":801.03,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":791.91,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I would stay away from the big financial services and be more regional retail, CPG and secondarily would be higher ed health services companies, hospitality and transportation.","index":213,"end_time":822.84,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":802.15,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So that''s the way I would break it down I think 2 billion to 50 billion in revenue.","index":214,"end_time":828.36,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":823.08,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"We can go sub a billion.","index":215,"end_time":831.32,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":829.8,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"It just you know it''s probably better.","index":216,"end_time":833.84,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":831.48,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"If it''s part of a larger portfolio.","index":217,"end_time":835.56,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":833.84,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Underneath you know a family officer or.","index":218,"end_time":839.25,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":836.65,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"A private equity or something like that.","index":219,"end_time":840.85,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":839.25,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So I think I would you know maybe make the floor a billion and.","index":220,"end_time":848.97,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":840.85,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"It''s a different motion when you go smaller but can be tailored for that.","index":221,"end_time":859.77,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":854.65,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right.","index":222,"end_time":860.57,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":860.17,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"We talked about cio, cd, IO, cto, cdo, heads of transformation platforms, engineering, apps, etc operations can also fit in there co sponsors.","index":223,"end_time":875.42,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":862.66,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I can give you all of this in writing so you have it.","index":224,"end_time":879.46,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":875.42,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"But also we want to talk about like triggers.","index":225,"end_time":886.34,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":881.3,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Do you want to hear about that now or do you want to wait?","index":226,"end_time":888.82,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":886.34,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, I mean we can dive.","index":227,"end_time":890.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":889.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Into that.","index":228,"end_time":891.04,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":890.64,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"New CIO expand.","index":229,"end_time":895.84,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":893.28,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So that''s one new enroll CIO, CTO.","index":230,"end_time":898.72,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":895.84,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Etc like 6 months recent hire.","index":231,"end_time":901.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":899.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, expanded scope.","index":232,"end_time":904.959,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":902.08,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So a larger role.","index":233,"end_time":906,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":904.959,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Also a big.","index":234,"end_time":909.68,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":908.88,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"One.","index":235,"end_time":910,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":909.68,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Going through some sort of modernization or know massive transformation.","index":236,"end_time":917.56,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":913.28,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"They''re s Linked to the market.","index":237,"end_time":918.76,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":917.56,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"That''s what they''re doing.","index":238,"end_time":919.72,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":918.76,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Margin pressure, cost value realization, that kind of thing.","index":239,"end_time":931.56,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":924.44,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And we have a.","index":240,"end_time":935.88,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":934.36,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"We''ll.","index":241,"end_time":936.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":936.2,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I''ll tell you more about this when we get into it but sort of a program rescue.","index":242,"end_time":941.08,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":936.56,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I''m going to say AI and data.","index":243,"end_time":944.5,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":942.9,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Everybody talks about AI and data.","index":244,"end_time":946.7,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":944.9,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So I think it''s really important to talk about how we talk about that because it is something we want to.","index":245,"end_time":958.139,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":946.7,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Talk about but I don''t know it''s.","index":246,"end_time":960.7,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":958.139,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Something that we will always lead with.","index":247,"end_time":964.1,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":960.7,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"It''s an embedded into whatever the strategy is as opposed to being the strategy itself.","index":248,"end_time":970.02,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":964.98,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right.","index":249,"end_time":970.74,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":970.5,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"If you any other question, any questions on that I can give you.","index":250,"end_time":981.42,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":976.74,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":251,"end_time":981.74,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":981.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So with the signals and this kind of bleeds also into like existing infrastructure, has there been any method that you guys are using to capture those signals?","index":252,"end_time":990.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":981.74,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Anything that''s delivering you anything automated of like hey this person just changed jobs or they''ve been talking a lot about modernization or you know they may be looking for margin relief.","index":253,"end_time":1001.49,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":990.5,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No Run any sort of formal campaigns and nothing that''s officially tracking that.","index":254,"end_time":1007.01,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1002.13,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"We did start to try and run a campaign for new in seat type leaders but the only mechanism we really have to pull that right now is using LinkedIn Sales Navigator and that only I''ll show you in seat for a year.","index":255,"end_time":1020.21,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1007.25,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"And I also don''t know based off of the list if it''s also pulling the trigger, if it''s just a much larger role within the organization or if that''s new to an organization.","index":256,"end_time":1031.07,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1021.25,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"So it takes a lot of combing through it and you also can''t export it.","index":257,"end_time":1035.35,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1032.19,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"So it''s been more of like a one off type trial trial for that.","index":258,"end_time":1039.35,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1035.35,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"So now especially so for that one specifically which I think would be our biggest target right now, there''s no sort of automated mechanism to do that today.","index":259,"end_time":1046.99,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1039.35,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Gotcha.","index":260,"end_time":1049.79,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1049.07,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Doug, were you you.","index":261,"end_time":1051.23,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1049.95,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Did you have a take on that as well?","index":262,"end_time":1053.31,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1051.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No, continue.","index":263,"end_time":1061.72,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1061.24,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Yeah, I''ll get it now.","index":264,"end_time":1063.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1062.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I just thought I heard you.","index":265,"end_time":1064.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1063.2,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I didn''t want to interrupt you or anything.","index":266,"end_time":1065.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1064.12,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":267,"end_time":1065.96,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1065.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And Carrie, we do have methods, you know.","index":268,"end_time":1068.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1065.96,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I know Justin kind of walked through the infrastructure of what we use for account based marketing and one of those does pick up signals for new job hires.","index":269,"end_time":1074.4,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1068.08,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We can set it at 3 months, 6 months, 12 months to automatically load into campaigns as well.","index":270,"end_time":1078.92,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1074.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Looking at the industries are there, you know we got.","index":271,"end_time":1083.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1080.44,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''ve got a lot right.","index":272,"end_time":1084.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1083.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we got manufacturing, got healthcare, we got fintech, there''s a few downstream, definitely not government.","index":273,"end_time":1091.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1084.38,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We would also talk about higher ed multi site would be a Factor in there.","index":274,"end_time":1094.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1091.62,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Are there any of these industries that you see move with more velocity than others?","index":275,"end_time":1099.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1095.06,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Doug, any thoughts on that?","index":276,"end_time":1105.62,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1103.78,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Are you thinking move from a sales cycle perspective?","index":277,"end_time":1110.2,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1106.66,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":278,"end_time":1110.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1110.2,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":279,"end_time":1110.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1110.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Like they''re, they''re the deal time, like the velocity of first conversation to close deal.","index":280,"end_time":1116.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1110.8,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think no.","index":281,"end_time":1121.4,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1119.48,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"In fact, what I''ve, what I''ve seen is a slowing of velocity across all.","index":282,"end_time":1126.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1121.64,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"People I talk to, honestly.","index":283,"end_time":1128.28,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1126.28,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I mean, certainly providers move very slow, usually the health care providers, because they.","index":284,"end_time":1133.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1128.28,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Have a different sort of academic often.","index":285,"end_time":1135.08,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1133.12,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"View of the world.","index":286,"end_time":1136.09,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1135.53,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Unless they''re for profit.","index":287,"end_time":1137.53,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1136.09,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"The manufacturing, because of their procurement processes.","index":288,"end_time":1148.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1139.45,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Can be very challenging to work with.","index":289,"end_time":1150.09,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1148.37,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I don''t, I don''t know that any are, are fast.","index":290,"end_time":1156.17,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1152.89,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I feel like the only ones that are, are just extremely immature from an organizational standpoint.","index":291,"end_time":1163.17,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1157.85,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"So there''s not as much red tape to go through, but.","index":292,"end_time":1166.01,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1163.17,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Right.","index":293,"end_time":1166.41,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1166.09,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"But they''re probably not your bottom line as much.","index":294,"end_time":1168.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1166.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, gotcha.","index":295,"end_time":1170.31,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1169.35,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And in those conversations, it''s often like a CIO or CISO or you know, one of those range of titles that you''re having that first conversation with.","index":296,"end_time":1177.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1170.95,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":297,"end_time":1178.39,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1177.99,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Typically the conversations are at the C level, maybe the C minus one.","index":298,"end_time":1182.39,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1178.39,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Okay.","index":299,"end_time":1183.15,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1182.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And it''s been a mix of like, you know, I know you talked a little bit about M and A as well, or them getting board pressure or pressuring to, to reduce their margins, clean up their costs.","index":300,"end_time":1192.75,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1183.15,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Or maybe they have leadership changes as, you know, and even with the modernization and new role and everything.","index":301,"end_time":1198.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1192.75,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Doug, that you had mentioned as well, are you seeing one more consistently than others that someone is willing to jump on a call?","index":302,"end_time":1204.65,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1198.57,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We''re only pushing.","index":303,"end_time":1208.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1206.41,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"We''re only pushing.","index":304,"end_time":1209.61,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1208.65,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Starting to push the new enroll narrative.","index":305,"end_time":1213.61,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1209.85,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"We''ve always been, you know, you got.","index":306,"end_time":1216.13,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1213.61,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"A problem, we can solve it very bespoke.","index":307,"end_time":1218.33,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1216.13,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Resonates with a few people, but it.","index":308,"end_time":1221.37,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1219.21,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Or people that we know because they know we can do it.","index":309,"end_time":1224.4,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1221.84,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"But that doesn''t resonate, as far as.","index":310,"end_time":1227.24,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1224.8,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I can tell with the market.","index":311,"end_time":1228.4,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1227.24,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So I don''t have enough data to tell you what the uptake is on the other offerings because I just haven''t.","index":312,"end_time":1233,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1228.4,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Really gone to market with them.","index":313,"end_time":1234.4,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1233,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right.","index":314,"end_time":1234.96,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1234.56,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"What I can say is the, the idea of starting to segment these into different offerings came late last year and I really don''t know.","index":315,"end_time":1249.45,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1235.2,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right.","index":316,"end_time":1250.25,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1249.93,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Which one is going to have the most interest.","index":317,"end_time":1253.13,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1250.25,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I think it''s really interesting to pressure test that.","index":318,"end_time":1256.53,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1253.37,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right.","index":319,"end_time":1256.89,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1256.53,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"To test it in the market and.","index":320,"end_time":1258.29,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1256.89,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"See.","index":321,"end_time":1258.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1258.29,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"You know, what.","index":322,"end_time":1262.25,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1260.57,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"What campaign works better.","index":323,"end_time":1264.57,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1262.889,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right.","index":324,"end_time":1265.29,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1264.89,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":325,"end_time":1266.01,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1265.61,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":326,"end_time":1266.25,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1266.01,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And that''s, that''ll be a.","index":327,"end_time":1267.29,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1266.25,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Obviously a very strong portion of our foundation that we''re establishing.","index":328,"end_time":1270.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1267.61,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Okay, great.","index":329,"end_time":1272.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1272.33,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"That''s great to understand.","index":330,"end_time":1273.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1272.97,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You know, you mentioned procurement getting in the way of some of these conversations as well.","index":331,"end_time":1277.85,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1274.09,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"How much impact, like from a timeline perspective is that several months, is it a year that it''s impacting the timeline?","index":332,"end_time":1285.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1279.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"What other portions of your conversations are being impacted by procurement?","index":333,"end_time":1289.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1285.66,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s, it can be a couple of weeks to a couple of months as a process.","index":334,"end_time":1296.38,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1291.66,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Depends on the size of your organization and the complexity.","index":335,"end_time":1299.34,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1296.62,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right.","index":336,"end_time":1300.14,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1299.74,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"And if we worked with them prior, etc.","index":337,"end_time":1303.02,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1300.3,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Because even, I mean, right now we''re still negotiating with a client that is an existing client.","index":338,"end_time":1307.54,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1303.02,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"So we already have the MSA done, but we still still have been going through iterations on, you know, scope and sow since, you know, early December.","index":339,"end_time":1316.44,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1307.54,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Right.","index":340,"end_time":1317.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1317.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And are you looking for all net new or are you looking also to, with the clients you''ve already landed with, expand opportunities through marketing?","index":341,"end_time":1324.52,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1318.04,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Expansion is obviously always great and making them aware that we''re not sort of a one trick pony for whatever it is they have worked with us for.","index":342,"end_time":1333.24,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1324.84,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"But we also don''t have a ton of clients either.","index":343,"end_time":1335.4,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1333.24,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"So expansion will not be the focus.","index":344,"end_time":1337.96,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1335.56,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"It''ll really be net new and becoming more of a market aware brand.","index":345,"end_time":1343.14,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1338.04,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Gotcha.","index":346,"end_time":1344.18,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1343.54,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Okay.","index":347,"end_time":1344.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1344.42,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And then Doug, you also mentioned AI and, and, and data.","index":348,"end_time":1348.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1345.14,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And every industry, I think has some sort of approach to this, some sort of thoughts on it.","index":349,"end_time":1353.86,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1348.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Are there any that you are particularly concerned about with AI being just a huge change to how they operate their business?","index":350,"end_time":1360.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1354.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I think it''s still, I think we''re in the trough of disillusionment in some degrees as it relates to AI.","index":351,"end_time":1373.51,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1363.62,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"A lot of companies spend a lot.","index":352,"end_time":1374.71,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1373.51,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Of money, didn''t get a lot of, you know, there were a bunch of reports out late last year on that.","index":353,"end_time":1379.63,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1374.71,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"However, we''re also seeing eyes, I''m sure you''re all doing as are we, right?","index":354,"end_time":1386.35,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1380.51,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Augmentation and the rise of, you know, orchestrated autonomy, autonomous agents that work together.","index":355,"end_time":1395.39,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1386.59,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And that is going to be a.","index":356,"end_time":1398.18,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1396.9,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I think a tectonic kind of shift, seismic shift in, in the landscape.","index":357,"end_time":1405.46,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1399.06,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"But so I think where, where I want to be careful is, you know, if I were to message and I''ll give you a couple of examples, I''ll give you two ends, three ends of.","index":358,"end_time":1422.22,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1405.46,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"A spectrum and I''m just, I''m riffing.","index":359,"end_time":1424.02,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1422.22,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Here and yeah, this is great.","index":360,"end_time":1425.58,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1424.02,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Yeah, Cyrus, you can chime in or.","index":361,"end_time":1428.62,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1425.74,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Or carry as well.","index":362,"end_time":1430.14,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1428.62,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So not for today''s conversation, but I.","index":363,"end_time":1434.66,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1431.66,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Have some relationships with some product companies that we will layer in some of.","index":364,"end_time":1440.54,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1434.66,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"The tooling into some of our offerings.","index":365,"end_time":1443.62,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1440.54,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"As well as have a referral agreement back to that product company for.","index":366,"end_time":1447.58,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1443.62,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"For.","index":367,"end_time":1450.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1450.34,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Additional commission based revenue if we''re not.","index":368,"end_time":1453.62,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1450.66,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Involved those, those companies do.","index":369,"end_time":1457.94,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1453.62,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"One is a conversational AI capability that is just would blow your mind and.","index":370,"end_time":1466.26,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1459.62,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"It is so good and even it''s.","index":371,"end_time":1469.02,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1466.26,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Sort of what we''ll call pilot research phase.","index":372,"end_time":1471.14,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1469.02,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I had a call with a, a guy I know from business school who leads for one of the largest pharma company on the planet.","index":373,"end_time":1483.68,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1472.9,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"He leads their pricing and negotiations team for the, the whole world.","index":374,"end_time":1488.04,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1483.68,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So his team manages market access and pricing and you know he''s got that undesirable role of maximizing profit for, for this company.","index":375,"end_time":1499.36,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1488.04,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Even though they''ve spent billions on AI.","index":376,"end_time":1506.24,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1504.08,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"He loved the conversational AI opportunity.","index":377,"end_time":1510,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1506.24,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So literally billions of dollars on AI.","index":378,"end_time":1512.8,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1510.08,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"They are incredibly mature.","index":379,"end_time":1514.8,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1513.12,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right.","index":380,"end_time":1515.52,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1515.12,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"However they need, you know, they can''t yet inject this new augmented capability into the human, into the human element, the.","index":381,"end_time":1528.04,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1516.96,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Bloodstream of the business which is where the conversational AI comes in.","index":382,"end_time":1531.46,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1528.04,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So very, very advanced.","index":383,"end_time":1535.77,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1534.09,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Not an AI native company, but very, very advanced in a, in a traditional company adopting it.","index":384,"end_time":1543.61,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1536.73,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right.","index":385,"end_time":1543.93,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1543.61,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"That''s one end of the spectrum.","index":386,"end_time":1546.01,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1544.57,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Likely we''re not going to have a ton of advisory opportunity there, but we have product opportunity.","index":387,"end_time":1550.97,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1546.09,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right.","index":388,"end_time":1551.69,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1551.29,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And it''s that door opener that I will literally kick a door down for and usually it works.","index":389,"end_time":1558.09,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1552.25,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right.","index":390,"end_time":1558.57,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1558.17,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So that also same thing happened at.","index":391,"end_time":1560.45,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1558.65,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Optum with a conversation with them yesterday.","index":392,"end_time":1562.69,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1560.45,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"We''re likely not going to get advisory work out of that, out of either of them right now.","index":393,"end_time":1569.56,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1564.68,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"But, but the product will be an entry point.","index":394,"end_time":1572.68,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1570.28,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"That''s the high end of maturity and complexity.","index":395,"end_time":1578.6,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1573.88,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And then on the low end you''ve.","index":396,"end_time":1580.36,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1578.68,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Got a manufacturer that is, you know.","index":397,"end_time":1583.88,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1580.36,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Suffering from tariff impacts in the US.","index":398,"end_time":1587.24,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1584.68,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Significant pressure on their margin.","index":399,"end_time":1590.2,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1587.48,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So they want to expand their margin.","index":400,"end_time":1592.2,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1590.36,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"While growing their top line and figuring out how to deal with tariffs.","index":401,"end_time":1598.27,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1593.23,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And while AI would be a game changer for them, they are so entrenched in how they operate and their GNA costs are really high and, and there''s a ton of opportunity there.","index":402,"end_time":1611.71,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1598.27,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"However, from a CIO''s perspective, they don''t have the budget so they''re actually the.","index":403,"end_time":1617.75,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1611.87,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Wrong buyer for it.","index":404,"end_time":1618.73,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1617.75,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"We also have to think about like, like the best conversations around AI I.","index":405,"end_time":1625.84,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1619.92,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Have are not with a cio.","index":406,"end_time":1627.52,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1625.84,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right, right.","index":407,"end_time":1629.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1627.84,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And so when you think about what the CIO generally is doing is they''re just struggling to figure out how do I do more with less where AI can help them do that.","index":408,"end_time":1638.8,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1629.04,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"That''s great, but they''re really not known these days.","index":409,"end_time":1642.6,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1638.8,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"As far as I can Tell as the leader of the AI adoption, it''s a business tool with business problems and most CIOs don''t, aren''t even seen as.","index":410,"end_time":1654.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1642.6,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"You know, capable of doing that.","index":411,"end_time":1657.29,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1654.81,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right.","index":412,"end_time":1657.77,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1657.37,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I''m not giving enough credit, but I''m pointing towards something I''m sensing in the market.","index":413,"end_time":1663.69,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1658.57,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And then somewhere in the middle is you''ve got, you know, a ton of, of activity but not a ton of value and so made a ton of investments.","index":414,"end_time":1679.66,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1666.09,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"They''ve stood up a council, maybe that council somewhat effective but you know, there is no cohesion and there''s now pressure.","index":415,"end_time":1689.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1679.66,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"From the board of.","index":416,"end_time":1690.02,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1689.14,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Okay, we tried this, we really need to figure this out.","index":417,"end_time":1693.98,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1690.02,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"What are you doing different.","index":418,"end_time":1694.98,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1693.98,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And then somewhere adjacent to that, and.","index":419,"end_time":1697.59,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1695.99,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I''ll give you another real life example is it''s a live foods company which.","index":420,"end_time":1702.99,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1697.59,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"We''Re, we have a good relationship into.","index":421,"end_time":1706.39,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1702.99,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"But haven''t yet been able to convert it.","index":422,"end_time":1708.63,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1706.39,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"They''re a 90 billion dollar company.","index":423,"end_time":1711.35,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1709.51,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"They have very clear operational kind of.","index":424,"end_time":1717.91,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1713.43,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Goals when it comes to maximizing the, the growth cycles of the chicken for optimal size and you know, size of the chicken breast and all that stuff and how much energy goes in to the process and what comes out of it.","index":425,"end_time":1735.07,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1718.07,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right.","index":426,"end_time":1735.39,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1735.07,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And then.","index":427,"end_time":1736.91,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1736.35,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"But I sat down with the COO.","index":428,"end_time":1739.63,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1737.95,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And I was like, well what.","index":429,"end_time":1740.83,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1739.63,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Tell me about your gna, tell me about your marketing, tell me about how you deal with pricing.","index":430,"end_time":1744.71,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1740.91,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And they had no strategy around that.","index":431,"end_time":1746.79,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1744.71,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Zero.","index":432,"end_time":1747.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1746.79,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"When it came to AI.","index":433,"end_time":1748.19,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1747.11,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Their only.","index":434,"end_time":1749.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1748.74,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"His only question to me was well, can I just do.","index":435,"end_time":1751.46,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1749.14,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I was giving him these ideas.","index":436,"end_time":1752.78,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1751.46,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"He''s like can I just put that.","index":437,"end_time":1754.22,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1752.78,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"In a co pilot?","index":438,"end_time":1755.22,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1754.22,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I said well no, but there are.","index":439,"end_time":1757.66,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1755.22,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Ways to do it.","index":440,"end_time":1758.3,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1757.66,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So there are.","index":441,"end_time":1759.38,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1758.3,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I guess what I''m trying to say is AI in general we''re going to.","index":442,"end_time":1764.499,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1760.42,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"See at the enterprise level in our.","index":443,"end_time":1767.3,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1764.499,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Target clients, you know, a few fun, you know, a few different points at which we might enter in a few different sets of problems.","index":444,"end_time":1777.46,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1767.3,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And we''ll need to get really specific to talk to those people about what are sort of like so they hear themselves and what we''re saying and then we have like a path forward for them.","index":445,"end_time":1786.99,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1777.95,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And so it really ranges.","index":446,"end_time":1788.91,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1787.23,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And you know, I don''t think any of them are things that I wouldn''t want to position for, especially now with the toolkit that we have and some of the relationships.","index":447,"end_time":1799.47,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1789.71,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"But, but there are probably some that we want to lean in on more.","index":448,"end_time":1804.87,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1799.47,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Because they''re going to be better for us from like growing our core business.","index":449,"end_time":1808.02,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1804.87,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right?","index":450,"end_time":1808.94,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1808.58,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean there''s some 80, 20 rule to some of this as well.","index":451,"end_time":1811.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1808.94,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Right.","index":452,"end_time":1812.26,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1811.94,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And what it sounds like is we''re probably going to want to set up multiple campaigns so that we can differentiate the messaging because these targets are going to care about different things, are going to have different pain points and they''re going to have different growth goals and we''re going to have to resonate with all of those.","index":453,"end_time":1826.02,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1813.22,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And so we can do enrichment for that as well.","index":454,"end_time":1828.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1826.02,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And I know you mentioned you didn''t want to.","index":455,"end_time":1830.38,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1828.98,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It wasn''t conversation for today, but it actually really goes into my segues, into my next portion of the conversation really well, which is diving into your guys offering your products and strategy or solution.","index":456,"end_time":1840.89,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1830.38,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I know, you know, reading through the website, you guys offer a lot.","index":457,"end_time":1844.41,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1840.89,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s strategy, it''s transformation, it''s AI, it''s cloud security, it''s talent, it''s interim leadership.","index":458,"end_time":1849.37,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1844.41,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So it''s, it''s not really about like, can they do it?","index":459,"end_time":1853.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1850.33,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I think it''s an understanding from prospects.","index":460,"end_time":1855.53,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1853.21,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You know, what do we even do?","index":461,"end_time":1857.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1855.93,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"What do I need?","index":462,"end_time":1858.97,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1857.85,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Where does this conversation start?","index":463,"end_time":1860.57,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1859.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And at the end of the day, if I want this, this and this, how can you still save me on cost?","index":464,"end_time":1864.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1860.57,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Is that kind of a lot of the conversations that you''re having initially as well?","index":465,"end_time":1868.26,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1864.98,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, Gotcha.","index":466,"end_time":1870.5,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1868.58,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Okay.","index":467,"end_time":1871.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1870.82,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And so I imagine like, you know, Carrie, you even said this.","index":468,"end_time":1874.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1871.22,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So maybe the pilot service that got them on board and we have like this opportunity to land and expand.","index":469,"end_time":1880.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1874.34,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Are you seeing one service more than others that is opening that door?","index":470,"end_time":1884.66,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1880.34,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, not really because again, it''s such a small sample size and it''s so relationship driven, which is why I think we''re kind of anxious to go and start with sort of the new IT leader and see how that resonates.","index":471,"end_time":1901.23,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1887.06,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Because some of our biggest accounts over the last two years have been a new in seat CIO that has a lot of big problems, a lot of big transformation, a lot of pressure from the board.","index":472,"end_time":1912.71,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1901.23,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"And that seems to be the best opportunity for us to get in quickly, add great value and then expand the relationship.","index":473,"end_time":1919.35,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1913.59,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"But yeah, again, it''s just kind of a bit of a small sample size.","index":474,"end_time":1923.07,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":1920.35,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah, I''d still like to tap into that data because, you know, if we have data, let''s, let''s, we can, you know, tie some additional research into that of course, and say like, we need to grow the amount of data that we''re working from, but it''s still great to have those signals early on.","index":475,"end_time":1936.47,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1923.31,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And you know, Doug, you kind of, I don''t know if it was jokingly mentioned or maybe it''s a pain point that you experience when talking to these people of them not really being capable of understanding beyond their role and understanding how businesses really need to drive their objective to adopt AI across the company.","index":476,"end_time":1953.98,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1936.47,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Things like that.","index":477,"end_time":1955.1,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1954.3,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Do you feel like, have you guys tried, like, educational resources for these people as they''re new in their role, or is it so new that we, like, haven''t built a one pager to send them over of how you can work with Acacia and how we can help you do X, Y and Z.","index":478,"end_time":1969.18,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1955.34,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Somewhere in between.","index":479,"end_time":1973.02,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1972.22,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So the educational resources.","index":480,"end_time":1974.7,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1973.1,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I like that.","index":481,"end_time":1975.66,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1974.78,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I''ll send you a pitch deck for Acacia.","index":482,"end_time":1978.54,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1976.22,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I''ll send you a pitch deck for the first 100 days offering so you can see them.","index":483,"end_time":1982.6,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1978.54,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":484,"end_time":1983.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1982.6,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Even walk you through that.","index":485,"end_time":1986.76,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1985.08,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I''m gonna put in the chat.","index":486,"end_time":1989.16,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1987.48,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"What?","index":487,"end_time":1990.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":1990.2,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"What?","index":488,"end_time":1994.04,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1993.64,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Team chat.","index":489,"end_time":1995.04,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":1994.2,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I don''t know how to use Zoom.","index":490,"end_time":1996.28,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1995.04,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I''m sorry, guys.","index":491,"end_time":1997.24,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1996.28,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Next.","index":492,"end_time":1997.56,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1997.24,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I''m, I apologize.","index":493,"end_time":1999.08,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":1997.56,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"No worries.","index":494,"end_time":2000.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":1999.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Really.","index":495,"end_time":2000.6,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2000.2,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"My name doesn''t even show up right.","index":496,"end_time":2002,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2000.6,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"But I, I, if you just click.","index":497,"end_time":2003.92,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2002,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"The chat, does the chat button show up for you?","index":498,"end_time":2006.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2003.92,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Are you in the app or just on, like, your browser?","index":499,"end_time":2008.65,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2006.28,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Sure.","index":500,"end_time":2009.04,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":2008.8,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"All right.","index":501,"end_time":2010.08,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2009.44,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"You just send us stuff afterward too.","index":502,"end_time":2015.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2013.28,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Don''t.","index":503,"end_time":2015.48,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2015.04,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Yeah, so no big deal.","index":504,"end_time":2017.12,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2015.48,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I, I, I went over the.","index":505,"end_time":2020.56,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2018.24,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Oh, I only get like a, a thousand.","index":506,"end_time":2025.44,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2023.44,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"All right.","index":507,"end_time":2026,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2025.52,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Anyway, I tried to paste something in here.","index":508,"end_time":2029.28,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2026,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Character limit.","index":509,"end_time":2030.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2029.36,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I got a character limit.","index":510,"end_time":2032.08,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2030.72,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So I''m going to share my screen with you.","index":511,"end_time":2039.13,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2033.2,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Am I perfect?","index":512,"end_time":2040.21,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2039.13,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Let''s see.","index":513,"end_time":2044.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2043.25,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And I''m really interested to dive into that first hundred days aspect as well.","index":514,"end_time":2053.73,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2049.73,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, well, I''m just like, I''m curious from my side, what is it about that first hundred days that is so critical?","index":515,"end_time":2065.82,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2055.49,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"And I think I, like, I, I can infer a lot of answers, but I actually want to just, like, hear the lot, like what your rationale is, because, I mean, I''m guessing, you know, they come in, you first don''t want to screw anything up, and then two, you want to roll out your ideas, but you want to make sure that they''re the right ideas.","index":516,"end_time":2087.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2065.82,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"But I''m curious from your perspective, like, that first hundred days, it seems like an incredibly critical time for this CIO comes in, they have to make some decisions, and this is a good time for Acacia to be involved.","index":517,"end_time":2102.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2088.04,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"And also, and I''m just going to say a couple of things here, I also think that whatever the pain point is, there might also be pain points for people who aren''t in their first hundred days.","index":518,"end_time":2112.28,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2102.2,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"But since we have that and we feel confident in it.","index":519,"end_time":2115.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2112.28,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Oh, this is great.","index":520,"end_time":2116.85,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2115.97,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"I''m glad I asked the question.","index":521,"end_time":2119.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2117.65,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"I''m looking at the.","index":522,"end_time":2119.97,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2119.21,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"At some of the answers.","index":523,"end_time":2120.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2119.97,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Let''s dig into her.","index":524,"end_time":2122.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2121.41,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":525,"end_time":2123.17,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2122.69,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"All right.","index":526,"end_time":2126.33,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2125.81,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Drew up the alley for you, Doug.","index":527,"end_time":2128.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2126.33,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"All right.","index":528,"end_time":2128.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2128.13,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Can you make it into, like, a full screen?","index":529,"end_time":2131.25,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":2128.61,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"I am sharing it full screen.","index":530,"end_time":2133.29,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2131.81,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I don''t know how to do.","index":531,"end_time":2134.17,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2133.29,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I don''t know how to.","index":532,"end_time":2135.65,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2134.17,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"It shows that I don''t.","index":533,"end_time":2140.53,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2136.13,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"There you go.","index":534,"end_time":2141.66,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":2141.18,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"There you go.","index":535,"end_time":2142.7,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2142.06,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"All right.","index":536,"end_time":2144.78,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2144.22,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So why.","index":537,"end_time":2151.18,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2150.54,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right.","index":538,"end_time":2151.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2151.58,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Mostly leaders have the least context when they start, yet the moves that they make are the most important.","index":539,"end_time":2161.82,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2153.9,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right.","index":540,"end_time":2162.7,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2162.3,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So they risk really acting too quickly and making decisions where it''s going to.","index":541,"end_time":2177.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2165.02,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Have, like, tissue rejection in the.","index":542,"end_time":2179.55,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2177.11,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"In the system.","index":543,"end_time":2180.31,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2179.55,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right.","index":544,"end_time":2181.27,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2180.87,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And at the same time, they''re going to be judged really quickly by the organization.","index":545,"end_time":2186.47,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2182.39,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So they''re sending signals.","index":546,"end_time":2189.47,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2187.83,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"They''re not getting enough.","index":547,"end_time":2190.75,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2189.47,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"They''re not listening and learning often enough.","index":548,"end_time":2193.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2190.75,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And especially in a technical role.","index":549,"end_time":2194.87,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2193.15,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And we really believe that the first.","index":550,"end_time":2199.79,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2198.27,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Hundred days really define the next thousand.","index":551,"end_time":2203.63,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2199.79,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And that''s the tagline.","index":552,"end_time":2205.23,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2203.79,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"We look at it from four dimensions.","index":553,"end_time":2208.91,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2206.91,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And generally our.","index":554,"end_time":2211.47,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2209.95,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"If they''re in a technical role, they''re going to all gravitate to the top left and sometimes to the bottom right.","index":555,"end_time":2218.03,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2211.71,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Okay.","index":556,"end_time":2218.91,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2218.27,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Rarely do I meet an individual who.","index":557,"end_time":2224.33,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2221.49,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Looks at all four of these dimensions with.","index":558,"end_time":2227.09,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2224.33,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Clarity.","index":559,"end_time":2231.73,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2231.09,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Okay.","index":560,"end_time":2233.25,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2232.69,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":561,"end_time":2234.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2233.65,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"There''s a gap somewhere.","index":562,"end_time":2234.93,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2234.01,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Right.","index":563,"end_time":2235.53,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2235.17,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And then look at the unspoken bargains call out.","index":564,"end_time":2238.33,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2235.53,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right.","index":565,"end_time":2238.69,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2238.33,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"The.","index":566,"end_time":2240.05,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2239.65,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"You see this time and time again, you.","index":567,"end_time":2244.61,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2240.21,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"It''s like joining a family.","index":568,"end_time":2245.93,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2244.61,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right, Right.","index":569,"end_time":2247.03,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2245.93,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Or, you know, everything looks cool from the outside until you get in and then, oh, wait, you know, this is.","index":570,"end_time":2253.91,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2247.03,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"What we have to live with.","index":571,"end_time":2254.79,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2253.91,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":572,"end_time":2255.27,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2254.79,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right.","index":573,"end_time":2255.91,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2255.51,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So.","index":574,"end_time":2257.67,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2257.27,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So these are the dimensions.","index":575,"end_time":2259.27,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2257.75,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"There are different ways in which you can land.","index":576,"end_time":2263.51,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2261.51,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So you know that I call it called out expanded role.","index":577,"end_time":2266.39,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2263.51,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So sometimes people come in in a relief role.","index":578,"end_time":2272.95,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2266.47,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right.","index":579,"end_time":2273.75,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2273.35,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So something happened last.","index":580,"end_time":2275.59,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2273.91,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Last person got let go for some reason or left on their own or.","index":581,"end_time":2281.71,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2276.23,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Maybe they''re coming in.","index":582,"end_time":2282.71,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2281.71,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Under a strong leader.","index":583,"end_time":2287.11,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2285.75,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Rebound and relief are different.","index":584,"end_time":2291.75,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2289.91,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Really.","index":585,"end_time":2295.75,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2295.35,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Rebound feels different because there''s not a mandate.","index":586,"end_time":2301.18,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2296.95,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"It''s more of.","index":587,"end_time":2305.18,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2304.14,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"You got to build confidence in the function.","index":588,"end_time":2307.18,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2305.18,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right.","index":589,"end_time":2307.66,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2307.26,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And I''ve seen this in the last.","index":590,"end_time":2309.42,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2308.06,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Two roles that one of our largest clients has taken.","index":591,"end_time":2312.7,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2309.42,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"One was a relief, and one was a rebound.","index":592,"end_time":2315.7,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2313.74,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And the expectations.","index":593,"end_time":2316.74,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2315.7,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And he didn''t realize it and I.","index":594,"end_time":2318.34,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2316.74,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Didn''T have this framework for him, are very different.","index":595,"end_time":2321.02,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2318.34,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And so it''s a very, very different entry point.","index":596,"end_time":2325.1,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2321.18,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And then there''s expanded road scope, so.","index":597,"end_time":2328.39,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2325.91,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"We call out what the traps are overloading.","index":598,"end_time":2333.59,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2330.95,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So you''re probably surprised to see that.","index":599,"end_time":2335.47,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2333.59,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I''m not talking about tech very much, are you?","index":600,"end_time":2337.99,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2335.47,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"A little bit.","index":601,"end_time":2339.43,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2338.55,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"If you Want to tackle that from your sales side, too?","index":602,"end_time":2342.55,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2340.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I mean, for me, I, I look at these slides.","index":603,"end_time":2345.59,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2342.79,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"I, I''m the owner of a professional services company.","index":604,"end_time":2349.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2345.59,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"I see a lot of similarities just in my, in what we see.","index":605,"end_time":2352.24,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2349.11,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Got to tell the story.","index":606,"end_time":2353.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2352.79,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":607,"end_time":2354.15,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2353.67,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"When CMOs come in, you know, I see a lot of similar, similar things.","index":608,"end_time":2359.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2355.19,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"You know, the predecessor failed, so they come in and they want to bring in an agency.","index":609,"end_time":2364.63,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2359.67,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"So that''s my first thing is I''m like, I like a lot of this, actually, because I see a lot of similarities.","index":610,"end_time":2371.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2364.63,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"And, you know, the people matter a lot when you''re selling professional services.","index":611,"end_time":2376.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2372.71,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"So what exactly is the solution that you''re selling?","index":612,"end_time":2380.57,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2377.19,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"It seems, you know that''s gonna come next, which will be interesting.","index":613,"end_time":2383.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2380.57,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":614,"end_time":2384.41,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2383.93,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Well, a little bit more setup and.","index":615,"end_time":2387.69,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2384.65,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Why it''s so important.","index":616,"end_time":2388.65,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2387.69,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"You feel like you have to move.","index":617,"end_time":2397.85,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2396.25,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Fast, but you have to move thoughtfully.","index":618,"end_time":2400.81,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2397.85,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And I think this is really important.","index":619,"end_time":2405.53,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2403.13,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"A lot of people miss this.","index":620,"end_time":2406.89,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2405.61,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So how do we approach it?","index":621,"end_time":2411.1,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2409.82,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Our, our approach is really designed to accelerate that understanding of what you''re in and what you inherited before you start to make decisions.","index":622,"end_time":2421.9,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2411.74,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And that''s really critical.","index":623,"end_time":2423.62,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2422.3,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"That''s the key bit.","index":624,"end_time":2424.94,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2423.62,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So they get an agenda, and so they''re still framed in like, I want a roadmap.","index":625,"end_time":2429.54,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2425.02,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"They''re asking me for a roadmap.","index":626,"end_time":2430.86,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2429.54,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"They''re going to ask me what my plans are.","index":627,"end_time":2432.3,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2430.86,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Okay, we''re going to get you that, that, but you got to do a lot of listening and learning before you do that.","index":628,"end_time":2438.46,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2432.3,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And so that''s what we, what we really set them up for.","index":629,"end_time":2443.66,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2439.58,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Real quick, Doug, before going to this slide, if you can go back.","index":630,"end_time":2447.9,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2445.42,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So I see.","index":631,"end_time":2449.94,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2449.26,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Sequence 90 day plan, is that in conclusion of the first 100 days?","index":632,"end_time":2453.34,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2449.94,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, I think it is.","index":633,"end_time":2455.7,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2454.46,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":634,"end_time":2455.98,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2455.7,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I mean, I, I, I don''t think It''ll take us 100 days to get there, but the, the, the, the most important thing is year one narrative.","index":635,"end_time":2465.08,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2455.98,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"But.","index":636,"end_time":2465.8,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2465.48,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Yeah, I''ll give you some timing here.","index":637,"end_time":2470.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2465.8,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"No, perfect.","index":638,"end_time":2472.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2472.12,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right.","index":639,"end_time":2473.56,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2473.16,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So we''re in six weeks.","index":640,"end_time":2479.72,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2474.44,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Yes.","index":641,"end_time":2483.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2483.24,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"You''ve diagnosed, you''ve mapped out everything, and you''ve already developed a framework by week six.","index":642,"end_time":2489.32,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2483.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":643,"end_time":2490.14,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2489.74,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And applying some of the tools that we have, I can even compress this.","index":644,"end_time":2494.7,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2490.22,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right.","index":645,"end_time":2496.22,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2495.82,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"If somebody says that''s too long, I.","index":646,"end_time":2499.14,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2496.78,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Can say, well, I can layer in, you know, the conversational AI.","index":647,"end_time":2502.78,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2499.14,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I can layer in some diagnostic tooling, and I can get you there in four to five.","index":648,"end_time":2509.18,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2503.1,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right.","index":649,"end_time":2511.26,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2510.86,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Because you see those stakeholder interviews.","index":650,"end_time":2513.5,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2511.58,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right.","index":651,"end_time":2514.7,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2514.3,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I can conduct those with my tool.","index":652,"end_time":2517.67,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2515.35,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Gotcha.","index":653,"end_time":2520.15,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2519.51,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So anyway, this is the package.","index":654,"end_time":2530.55,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2528.63,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I mean, it''s, I I''d love for you to pressure test it.","index":655,"end_time":2535.71,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2531.99,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And it, as I said, like this could work with any leader.","index":656,"end_time":2538.63,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2535.71,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"It doesn''t.","index":657,"end_time":2539.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2538.63,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"This was founded in research, had nothing to do with a tech leader.","index":658,"end_time":2541.81,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2539.11,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I mean, the key is we''re a technology.","index":659,"end_time":2545.88,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2543.32,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"We''re at the elbow support for CIOs, CTOs, CDOs, you know, whatever.","index":660,"end_time":2552.2,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2546.68,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So we''re of course going to bring the lens of the technical expertise.","index":661,"end_time":2557.48,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2552.36,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right.","index":662,"end_time":2558.44,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2558.04,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"But where I think it differs from what, and I don''t know this for a fact, Deloitte does have like a leadership, leadership trends for make transition support called Deloitte Labs.","index":663,"end_time":2569.48,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2559.64,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"That''s probably what we would compete against.","index":664,"end_time":2573.47,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2571.07,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"But I think, I don''t know how they price.","index":665,"end_time":2575.39,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2573.47,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I don''t know what, you know, I.","index":666,"end_time":2576.67,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2575.47,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Don''T know enough about it, but I don''t think that, you know, I''m hoping.","index":667,"end_time":2580.79,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2576.67,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"We, we wedge against it like, or, or outside of that range.","index":668,"end_time":2584.91,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2580.79,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right, right.","index":669,"end_time":2586.03,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2584.99,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"What I want people to feel is that they''re getting like incredibly high quality analysis and, and guidance that will keep them out of hot water and help them make the best decisions quickly.","index":670,"end_time":2604.44,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2589.47,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right.","index":671,"end_time":2605.32,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2604.92,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And, and set themselves up for a.","index":672,"end_time":2608.16,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2605.32,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Really highly successful, you know, three, four years.","index":673,"end_time":2614.04,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2608.16,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right.","index":674,"end_time":2614.92,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2614.52,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I have to imagine that this presentation was born out of just several conversations you''ve had.","index":675,"end_time":2619.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2615.16,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And you''re like, I need something that really educates them on what they''re dealing with.","index":676,"end_time":2623.24,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2619.84,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Is that fair, accurate and not accurate?","index":677,"end_time":2627.81,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2625.17,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":678,"end_time":2628.53,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2628.05,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Okay.","index":679,"end_time":2629.17,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2628.61,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And, and yeah, I mean, to your point, I mean, when you''re talking to, you know, IT companies, whether they call themselves consultants, advisors, whatever flavor that they like to be and position themselves as, I mean, a lot of offerings are table stakes at a certain point.","index":680,"end_time":2643.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2630.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So it''s about how can we differentiate ourselves, how can we look at this through a different lens and how do we, you know, stand out from the crowd?","index":681,"end_time":2649.09,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2643.09,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And that is exactly what I wanted to do.","index":682,"end_time":2652.71,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2650.71,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Yep.","index":683,"end_time":2653.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2652.71,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And it wasn''t like I came up.","index":684,"end_time":2656.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2654.79,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"With this stuff on my own.","index":685,"end_time":2657.19,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2656.15,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And I work with an organizational psychologist.","index":686,"end_time":2659.59,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2657.19,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"This is his expertise.","index":687,"end_time":2660.79,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2659.59,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I have, you know, now we have the tooling that we can lever in to do this.","index":688,"end_time":2665.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2660.79,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I''ve seen a bunch of failed transitions.","index":689,"end_time":2667.67,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2665.27,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I''ve seen people do it really well.","index":690,"end_time":2669.51,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2667.67,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And this is always going to be a factor because this is one thing that doesn''t change the average lifespan of a CIO is.","index":691,"end_time":2676.07,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2670.47,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I forget what the number is, but.","index":692,"end_time":2677.51,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2676.07,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"It''S, you know, two years, maybe two and a half, something like that.","index":693,"end_time":2681.51,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2677.51,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":694,"end_time":2682.31,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":2681.83,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Not, not very long.","index":695,"end_time":2683.91,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2682.31,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":696,"end_time":2684.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2684.07,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Before something goes wrong or business needs shifts or a new opportunity comes up.","index":697,"end_time":2690.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2686.87,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":698,"end_time":2691.95,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2690.95,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Exactly.","index":699,"end_time":2692.55,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2691.95,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Excuse me.","index":700,"end_time":2694.63,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2693.91,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Oh, go ahead, continue, Doug.","index":701,"end_time":2697.31,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2695.99,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Sorry, are.","index":702,"end_time":2698.35,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":2697.31,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Are we.","index":703,"end_time":2698.87,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2698.35,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"We have 15 minutes left.","index":704,"end_time":2701.35,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2699.67,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"We have 15 minutes.","index":705,"end_time":2702.23,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2701.35,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":706,"end_time":2702.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2702.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Can I share one more thing with you?","index":707,"end_time":2704.76,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2703.44,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Yeah, go ahead.","index":708,"end_time":2705.44,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2704.76,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":709,"end_time":2705.84,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2705.44,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"In the meantime, can I ask you a question, please.","index":710,"end_time":2708.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2705.92,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"What is your appetite or lack thereof to create content?","index":711,"end_time":2717.6,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2709.92,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"If we made it really easy for you and we stood something up where you could talk to CIOs and we could create a bunch of materials out of those conversations, the reason I ask there, we.","index":712,"end_time":2733.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2717.76,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"We.","index":713,"end_time":2733.61,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2733.25,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"The stories that you can tell and the expertise that you can demonstrate is incredibly powerful when it comes like Colin said, you''re gonna see a bunch of people out there offering from a table stakes perspective.","index":714,"end_time":2749.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2733.61,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"The same thing when you''re a professional services company and you can tell your stories, you can engage and interact with the types of individuals that you want to be selling to.","index":715,"end_time":2760.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2749.37,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"It''s incredibly powerful for marketing.","index":716,"end_time":2764.26,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2761.54,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"So I''m curious, Doug, if we were to set up some sort of ongoing series or something, and this could be Carrie, Cyrus, whomever, but I think it would be powerful.","index":717,"end_time":2775.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2764.74,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Are you all up for that?","index":718,"end_time":2777.46,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2775.94,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Are you like.","index":719,"end_time":2778.18,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2777.46,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"No, I like to do my thing and I don''t want to contribute to like content creation.","index":720,"end_time":2785.78,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2778.26,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"I just am curious your appetite or lack thereof of something along those lines.","index":721,"end_time":2791.06,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2785.94,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"I think we''re, we would be willing to try just about anything.","index":722,"end_time":2798.1,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2791.94,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So the answer is absolutely, I. I can precede it with.","index":723,"end_time":2809.9,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2800.1,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I use a bunch of different.","index":724,"end_time":2811.58,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2809.9,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"As you can tell, I''ve got chat GPT up right now, but I also use Claude cowork.","index":725,"end_time":2815.5,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2811.58,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I had it go through all of.","index":726,"end_time":2819.3,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2817.1,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"My files last night on my computer.","index":727,"end_time":2821.86,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2819.3,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Organize them as well as categorize them into things that could be used for frameworks for go to market for sales.","index":728,"end_time":2830.34,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2821.86,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Because we, you know, I''ve got thousands of documents from the last 11 years of doing delivery.","index":729,"end_time":2835.42,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2830.34,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And, and so that, that slide deck I just showed you, you know, it didn''t happen in, in a two minute prompt with Claude, but it, it came from.","index":730,"end_time":2849.25,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2836.45,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And right now Claude''s building for these other five the same thing for you.","index":731,"end_time":2856.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2850.21,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So you''ll have it.","index":732,"end_time":2856.89,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2856.05,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"But I''m, I''m all about content, actually.","index":733,"end_time":2861.09,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2856.89,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I''m excited.","index":734,"end_time":2862.29,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2861.49,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So last night I was sent by.","index":735,"end_time":2867.79,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2862.37,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"The founder of the conversational AI company.","index":736,"end_time":2871.23,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2867.79,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"A loom video that he had done for one of his prospects where he was basically.","index":737,"end_time":2877.15,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2871.63,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Having a conversation with her, with the conversational AI agent about how.","index":738,"end_time":2884.59,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2879.31,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"It works and what it does.","index":739,"end_time":2885.79,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2884.59,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And it was, excuse my language, fascinating.","index":740,"end_time":2889.39,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2885.79,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Like it blew my mind and I am confident, like, and not just the technology.","index":741,"end_time":2897.93,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2889.39,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So let''s put the technology Aside for a second.","index":742,"end_time":2900.25,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2898.09,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"As you can tell, I''m really excited about it.","index":743,"end_time":2901.73,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2900.25,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"But I''m right there with you.","index":744,"end_time":2903.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":2901.73,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, Colin messaged me.","index":745,"end_time":2906.249,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2903.93,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"I think Claude was just down.","index":746,"end_time":2907.33,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2906.249,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"He''s like well how do I live there?","index":747,"end_time":2909.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2907.33,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Yeah, so co work for Claude on your Mac.","index":748,"end_time":2917.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2912.17,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"If you have Macs, assuming you do, if you''re marketing the is great and I''ll show you that in a second.","index":749,"end_time":2926.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2917.05,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"What I have what I had to.","index":750,"end_time":2927.09,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":2926.05,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Do but for, for me that Loom video that he had was just, was amazing and really, really special.","index":751,"end_time":2937.85,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2927.09,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And so I, I think whatever the medium, the format, even if we were to do follow ups with, you know, with folks using Loom, I like that as another option.","index":752,"end_time":2952.66,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2939.05,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So yes, conversations.","index":753,"end_time":2955.78,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2952.74,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Yes.","index":754,"end_time":2956.38,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2955.94,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Different medium.","index":755,"end_time":2957.22,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2956.38,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Yes.","index":756,"end_time":2957.78,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2957.38,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Different, you know, things sharing stories as you can tell.","index":757,"end_time":2961.42,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2957.78,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I like to tell stories.","index":758,"end_time":2962.46,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2961.42,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So yeah, let''s, let''s figure it out.","index":759,"end_time":2964.58,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":2962.46,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I wrote a, I wrote a post on this two days ago on LinkedIn.","index":760,"end_time":2969.1,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2966.1,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"If we''re not connected, we should be.","index":761,"end_time":2970.22,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2969.1,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"But just talking about how executive leadership sometimes doesn''t want to be involved in content creation and they tell marketing, just go do it.","index":762,"end_time":2977.42,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2970.22,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"And I don''t believe that that''s how companies actually grow.","index":763,"end_time":2979.66,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2977.42,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"You gotta, people want to buy from you know, Cyrus, Carrie, Doug, Colin and I can sit here and put together great marketing campaigns.","index":764,"end_time":2988.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2979.98,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"But the reality is and especially when you''re a professional services company, people want to hear from the people doing the work who, what kind of, you know, what kind of minds do you have, how do you think, how do you operate?","index":765,"end_time":2999.9,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":2988.86,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"And you know one of the things that we do for a lot of our clients is we have these, these video series.","index":766,"end_time":3007.04,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3001.52,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Whether it is somebody talking to camera, somebody talking to an AI agent or somebody talking to people within the space, there''s a lot of different things we can do.","index":767,"end_time":3014.76,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3007.44,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"We''ll pick your brain on how you want to approach something like that.","index":768,"end_time":3018.4,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3014.76,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"And then yeah, I mean Looms.","index":769,"end_time":3020.56,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3018.96,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"I think Colin and I both have the Loom plugin sitting right on our, on our desktop.","index":770,"end_time":3026.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3020.56,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"So we''re all speaking the same language here which is very exciting.","index":771,"end_time":3029.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3026.4,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"We actually just built an internal app for ourselves using Claude code.","index":772,"end_time":3033.03,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3030.15,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"So it''s fun to talk to you guys and kind of hear, you know, how your perspective.","index":773,"end_time":3037.67,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3033.03,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Yeah, no, likewise.","index":774,"end_time":3039.35,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3038.07,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So good.","index":775,"end_time":3042.789,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3040.95,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I''m glad to hear it and looking forward to more.","index":776,"end_time":3046.39,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3042.789,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I do have these.","index":777,"end_time":3050.87,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3049.83,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I guess we''ve got them now into.","index":778,"end_time":3052.91,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3051.51,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Seven areas for go to market.","index":779,"end_time":3057.85,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3052.91,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"You''ll get this.","index":780,"end_time":3060.81,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3059.77,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I assume you''re using some sort of a assistant whether Claude or whomever.","index":781,"end_time":3067.09,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3062.01,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So I''m going to send it to you in Markdown.","index":782,"end_time":3069.05,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3067.09,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Perfect.","index":783,"end_time":3070.01,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3069.45,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"You''ll see a lot comes from me in Markdown.","index":784,"end_time":3073.13,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3071.13,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I''ll send you slides as well.","index":785,"end_time":3074.41,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3073.13,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"But I.","index":786,"end_time":3075.45,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3074.41,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Yeah, and Doug, it''ll be good for you also to just share the output of all the conversations we had shared around, you know, our, our thinking around go to market approach, what should be, what we lead with, who are our top competitors, what stands us apart from them, you know, all of those pieces.","index":787,"end_time":3097.38,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":3077.45,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"So if you can share that document too, that would be good when you''re sharing this.","index":788,"end_time":3101.22,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":3098.02,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Yeah, I, I will.","index":789,"end_time":3103.3,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3102.02,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"It''ll actually to some degree be appended.","index":790,"end_time":3109.42,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3103.3,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Here because this is kind of a.","index":791,"end_time":3110.86,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3109.42,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Summary running summary of all of those things.","index":792,"end_time":3113.86,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3110.86,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"But yeah, and this does live to some degree in a site that I''ll just give you both access to, which is a Manus generated site.","index":793,"end_time":3126.66,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3115.22,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"But it hasn''t really been refreshed in a bit.","index":794,"end_time":3128.82,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3126.66,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So take it with a grain of salt.","index":795,"end_time":3131.38,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3128.82,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"But it outlines at least five of.","index":796,"end_time":3135.35,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3133.39,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"These areas here.","index":797,"end_time":3138.35,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3135.35,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And you''ll have access.","index":798,"end_time":3142.11,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3140.27,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"To that as well.","index":799,"end_time":3143.39,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3142.19,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"The, the other thing I wanted to show you.","index":800,"end_time":3151.79,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3147.71,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Is.","index":801,"end_time":3157.95,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3157.55,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I''ll just show you that site real quick and then I''ll.","index":802,"end_time":3163.12,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3160.64,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"You guys talk.","index":803,"end_time":3164.72,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3163.76,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Do you have any questions for me?","index":804,"end_time":3166.48,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3164.72,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Yeah, well, I was going to say we have, we have about eight minutes left, so I''m very interested to see what you have to show.","index":805,"end_time":3171.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3167.12,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then Carrie, if you''re good with it for like my marketing current infrastructure setup questions, I''ll just send those over to you and if you could give me a response, that would be great.","index":806,"end_time":3179.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3171.48,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, absolutely.","index":807,"end_time":3180.88,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":3179.92,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"This is great though.","index":808,"end_time":3184.08,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3183.04,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"I just slacked Colin on the side and said you have more stuff than like big companies that we talk to.","index":809,"end_time":3194.01,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3187.21,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"So.","index":810,"end_time":3195.13,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3194.73,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And I think that that''s our best engagements are with people who are scrappy.","index":811,"end_time":3200.13,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3195.37,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"You know, you''re clearly trying to put things together yourself.","index":812,"end_time":3202.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3200.13,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"You have ideas, it creates a very collaborative environment.","index":813,"end_time":3206.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3202.81,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"And so we''re excited to see all of this stuff and then be able to lend some of our expertise to it as well.","index":814,"end_time":3214.37,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3207.69,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"So this is, this is great stuff.","index":815,"end_time":3216.45,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3214.45,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Fantastic.","index":816,"end_time":3217.81,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3216.93,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Well, good.","index":817,"end_time":3220.37,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3219.81,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And I''m.","index":818,"end_time":3220.93,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3220.37,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I''m getting a good vibe from you guys.","index":819,"end_time":3223.05,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3221.09,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So looking forward to it.","index":820,"end_time":3224.13,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3223.05,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So what you''ll get access to this?","index":821,"end_time":3226.53,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3224.13,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I might do one quick refresh and just know that it''ll go.","index":822,"end_time":3230.93,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3227.57,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"But you''ll see sort of our hypothesis where we want to position ourselves, what.","index":823,"end_time":3239.28,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3230.93,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"The converging forces are.","index":824,"end_time":3240.84,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3239.28,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Why we think.","index":825,"end_time":3243.68,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3243.08,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"We''Re built for it.","index":826,"end_time":3244.68,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3243.68,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Who we are.","index":827,"end_time":3249.4,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3248.6,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I think this is really going to be helpful.","index":828,"end_time":3254.12,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3251.88,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"It''s got some definition of the icps.","index":829,"end_time":3256.36,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3254.28,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And right now there are kind of like three high level.","index":830,"end_time":3262.24,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3259.24,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"But you know, there are more than.","index":831,"end_time":3265,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3262.24,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"That when you start to go into verticals.","index":832,"end_time":3266.67,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3265,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"We have offerings so tiered.","index":833,"end_time":3274.82,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3269.14,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"You''ll see first hundred days security and resilience, AI readiness, structural offers and other targeted offerings, how they fit together.","index":834,"end_time":3286.98,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3274.9,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"There''s some first stab at like a go to market and the different campaigns.","index":835,"end_time":3295.52,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3289.3,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"None of which we''ve really won.","index":836,"end_time":3296.88,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3295.52,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And then some details on some frameworks.","index":837,"end_time":3299.96,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3297.6,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I would just really focus on the strategy, who we are, the offerings.","index":838,"end_time":3305.76,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3299.96,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And.","index":839,"end_time":3308,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3307.6,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Know that this won''t be fully aligned to the.","index":840,"end_time":3311.36,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3308,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I mean it''ll be pretty close.","index":841,"end_time":3312.96,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3311.6,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I''ll have Manus do one more rebuild, but like you''ll, you''ll have this.","index":842,"end_time":3317.36,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3313.52,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So you can kind of walk through it and you can also make a comment and you can also ask questions.","index":843,"end_time":3324.2,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3317.36,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"So there''s an LLM behind this that.","index":844,"end_time":3326.72,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3324.76,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Has all the, all the data.","index":845,"end_time":3328.04,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3326.72,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"This is awesome.","index":846,"end_time":3330.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3329.4,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":847,"end_time":3330.92,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3330.44,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Thank you for, thank you for building this.","index":848,"end_time":3333.8,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3331.88,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"As Justin said, we normally get like, I don''t know, guys, we just need more leads.","index":849,"end_time":3337.72,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3333.8,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Figure it out.","index":850,"end_time":3338.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3337.8,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"We don''t even know who we need to talk to.","index":851,"end_time":3340.36,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3338.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So you''re obviously handing over a lot more information than that, which is going to streamline this.","index":852,"end_time":3345.04,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3341.08,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, Was that.","index":853,"end_time":3346.81,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3345.04,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"So Manus.","index":854,"end_time":3348.33,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3347.13,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":855,"end_time":3349.69,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3349.21,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"What is the intention behind that?","index":856,"end_time":3351.49,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3349.69,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Is that the new.","index":857,"end_time":3352.25,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3351.49,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Is that a new site?","index":858,"end_time":3353.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3352.33,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Is that just something you''re using in the background?","index":859,"end_time":3355.21,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3353.21,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"What, internal knowledge base?","index":860,"end_time":3357.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3355.45,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, internal knowledge base.","index":861,"end_time":3359.29,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3357.77,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":862,"end_time":3360.97,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3360.49,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Yeah, that''s really solid.","index":863,"end_time":3364.17,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3362.01,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"That could help people a lot.","index":864,"end_time":3365.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3364.17,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"See a lot of that information.","index":865,"end_time":3366.89,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3365.93,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Yeah, Yeah.","index":866,"end_time":3369.09,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3368.01,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I mean it''s I.","index":867,"end_time":3370.73,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3369.09,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And the, the.","index":868,"end_time":3371.69,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3370.73,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"If the cool thing is when you added it, when I added the LLM.","index":869,"end_time":3375.74,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3372.46,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"In the background, then if you had a question about, well, why did you choose this?","index":870,"end_time":3379.62,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3375.74,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Right.","index":871,"end_time":3379.94,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3379.62,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"It''ll print come back with the research that I, I conducted to say that.","index":872,"end_time":3384.46,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3379.94,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"And so that''s what''s feeding that chatbot.","index":873,"end_time":3386.54,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3384.46,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Is that knowledge base.","index":874,"end_time":3387.58,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3386.54,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":875,"end_time":3389.26,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3388.62,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"I don''t know if I can put you and Colin in the same room together.","index":876,"end_time":3392.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3390.3,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"I don''t know if marketing will happen.","index":877,"end_time":3394.7,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3393.26,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"A lot of talking about how these tools all work together.","index":878,"end_time":3399.35,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3396.38,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"No, that, that''s great.","index":879,"end_time":3400.87,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3399.35,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"We''re going to be using.","index":880,"end_time":3401.99,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3401.11,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"And Colin, you could probably speak to it more than I can.","index":881,"end_time":3404.39,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3402.15,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"We''re going to be using a handful of different LLMs as well on our side that we''ve custom built as part of our building of the roadmap.","index":882,"end_time":3412.83,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3404.87,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"You know, there''s this intake of talking to you all, which is incredibly important, but then there''s also us going and seeing what other people are doing, what are your competitors doing and then how can we differentiate and find lanes to win?","index":883,"end_time":3424.93,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3412.83,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"But Colin, I''m.","index":884,"end_time":3426.53,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3425.65,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Stop talking.","index":885,"end_time":3426.93,"speaker_id":3,"start_time":3426.53,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"You got four minutes left.","index":886,"end_time":3428.05,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3426.93,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Yeah, yeah.","index":887,"end_time":3428.77,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3428.29,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I mean, just to touch on that.","index":888,"end_time":3429.69,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3428.77,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So we do a massive research document.","index":889,"end_time":3431.61,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3429.69,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"It''s so we''re scraping your competitors, your website, all of their social media pages, what they run from a paid advertising perspective, how strong their brand and offerings are, and we develop a full matrix for it because it opens up what your market opportunities are based on research.","index":890,"end_time":3447.21,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3431.61,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And then combine that with our conversations that we have to date, which then lead into our roadmap, which is what we suggest laying out for annual goals and down to the exact task that we''re going to do for the first three months.","index":891,"end_time":3459.63,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3447.21,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"So that''s, that''s all what comes in the roadmap.","index":892,"end_time":3462.71,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3460.67,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And so if you can send all the documents that you alluded to over.","index":893,"end_time":3466.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3462.71,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And Carrie, like I said, I''ll follow up with some more marketing based questions about just different tools that you guys have in place.","index":894,"end_time":3472.59,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3467.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"What I would like to do is get our next meeting on the calendar, which is the alignment meeting in between now and then we''ll conduct some research, look through everything you send over.","index":895,"end_time":3480.76,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3473.23,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"If we can get access to the CRM and just make numbers match on our side, we''ll come in with a few questions and then that leads to a really strong roadmap meeting using pipe drive.","index":896,"end_time":3490.48,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3480.76,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"What did you tell me you''re using, Carrie?","index":897,"end_time":3492.32,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3490.64,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Yeah, pipedrive.","index":898,"end_time":3493.44,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":3492.4,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Okay.","index":899,"end_time":3494,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3493.44,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":900,"end_time":3496.56,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3495.92,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Do you guys want to book that meeting now or.","index":901,"end_time":3498.08,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3496.64,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Carrie, do you want me to send over another like, availability link?","index":902,"end_time":3500.64,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3498.08,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah, if you want to send the availability link and then I can look across.","index":903,"end_time":3504.32,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":3501.68,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Across calendars.","index":904,"end_time":3505.44,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":3504.48,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Okay, you and me call.","index":905,"end_time":3507.92,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3505.76,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Yeah, sure thing.","index":906,"end_time":3509.2,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3507.92,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"All right, great.","index":907,"end_time":3510.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3510,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Well, with the last roughly 90 seconds that we have here, were there any questions or anything that you guys had before we kind of go into our async, look at a bunch of data and information and then come back to the table with our next meeting?","index":908,"end_time":3520.88,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3510.56,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"No, I''m good.","index":909,"end_time":3524.64,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3523.2,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"All right, awesome.","index":910,"end_time":3527.04,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3526.16,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"All right, well, I''ll follow up with that email and I''ll include all of you on it.","index":911,"end_time":3531.84,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3527.36,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"And Doug?","index":912,"end_time":3532.56,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3531.84,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Yeah.","index":913,"end_time":3532.88,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3532.56,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Whenever you have a chance, just reply with all the documents that you''re sharing.","index":914,"end_time":3535.83,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3532.88,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"You got it.","index":915,"end_time":3537.98,"speaker_id":0,"start_time":3537.26,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"Awesome.","index":916,"end_time":3538.62,"speaker_id":4,"start_time":3538.14,"speaker_name":"Douglas SMith"},{"text":"All right, well, thank you guys so much for your time.","index":917,"end_time":3540.22,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3538.62,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"I hope you have a great rest of your day.","index":918,"end_time":3541.5,"speaker_id":2,"start_time":3540.22,"speaker_name":"Colin Costigan"},{"text":"Thanks everyone.","index":919,"end_time":3542.3,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3541.58,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"Appreciate it.","index":920,"end_time":3543.34,"speaker_id":5,"start_time":3542.62,"speaker_name":"Kerry Marker"},{"text":"Take care.","index":921,"end_time":3543.94,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3543.42,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"},{"text":"See ya.","index":922,"end_time":3544.54,"speaker_id":1,"start_time":3543.94,"speaker_name":"Justin Brown"}],"dateString":"2026-01-22T16:30:00.000Z","host_email":"colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com","meeting_link":"https://us02web.zoom.us/j/86149189126?pwd=DaHy4wIGxB0N93hUPm3AQFZhYuA2gP.1&jst=2","participants":["colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com,dhsmith@chooseacacia.com,cclemensen@chooseacacia.com,tristan.pelligrino@marketersindemand.com,kmarker@chooseacacia.com,justin.brown@marketersindemand.com","dhsmith@chooseacacia.com","cclemensen@chooseacacia.com","tristan.pelligrino@marketersindemand.com","kmarker@chooseacacia.com","justin.brown@marketersindemand.com"],"transcript_url":"https://app.fireflies.ai/view/01KFECHXBBKV6KA36PZCK3CDCT","organizer_email":"colin.costigan@marketersindemand.com"}'::jsonb,
    '{"label":"positive","confidence":0.95,"bullets":["Defined clear ideal client profile: $1–$50B revenue, multi-site, non-government, CIO/CTO targets.","Aligned on ''first 100 days'' service as key wedge offering for new IT leadership.","Agreed to develop segmented campaigns tailored to buyer triggers like modernization or margin pressure.","Discussed pipeline limitations and intent to prioritize net-new lead generation over client expansion.","Confirmed strong client appetite and readiness for collaborative content and marketing efforts."],"highlights":[{"quote":"Lead generation is a top priority and everything else is going to operate in service of that.","speaker":"Colin Costigan"},{"quote":"I think we would be willing to try just about anything.","speaker":"Douglas SMith"},{"quote":"We''re sort of at that inflection point...that isn''t sustainable, especially for the level of growth that we''re looking for.","speaker":"Kerry Marker"}],"topics":["go-to-market","lead generation","ideal customer","content","AI"],"model":"openai/gpt-4-turbo","version":1,"generated_at":"2026-01-22T00:00:00Z"}'::jsonb,
    '{"fireflies_summary":{"notes":"## **Target Market Definition**\n\nThe team agreed to focus on **target organizations between $1 billion and $50 billion in revenue**, prioritizing verticals like manufacturing, retail, consumer packaged goods, healthcare, fintech, and excluding government clients (10:14).  \n- **Douglas Smith** emphasized tailoring lower-revenue targets (sub-$1 billion) when part of larger portfolios such as private equity holdings.  \n- The ideal contacts are **CIOs, CTOs, CISOs, and their direct reports**, with an emphasis on new or recently expanded roles as key triggers for engagement.  \n- Market complexity and deal velocity vary by vertical, with healthcare providers and manufacturing having slower sales cycles due to procurement and organizational factors (18:30).  \n- Expansion within existing clients is secondary; the primary goal is **net new client acquisition** and building broader market awareness (22:04).\n\n## **Lead Generation and Signal Capture Strategy**\n\nThe firm currently lacks automated methods to capture real-time signals such as new leadership hires or modernization efforts, relying on manual LinkedIn Sales Navigator searches without export capabilities (16:21).  \n- **Colin Costigan** noted their own use of account-based marketing tools capable of detecting signals like new job hires within customizable timeframes (3, 6, 12 months) to automate campaign targeting (17:42).  \n- Multiple segmented campaigns will be required to address diverse pain points and growth priorities across different buyer personas, supporting differentiated messaging (30:08).  \n- Procurement delays of **weeks to months** affect deal timelines, necessitating a realistic sales cycle approach (21:31).\n\n## **First Hundred Days Offering and Strategic Differentiation**\n\nAcacia’s **First Hundred Days service** targets new technical leaders to help them make informed decisions quickly while avoiding costly missteps, a critical window that shapes their long-term success (35:41).  \n- The approach is grounded in research and refined with organizational psychology expertise to address typical leadership challenges beyond technology alone (43:24).  \n- The offering delivers a **year-one narrative and roadmap within six weeks**, compressible to 4-5 weeks using diagnostic tools and AI-enhanced stakeholder interviews (41:23).  \n- Differentiation relies on high-quality analysis, leadership transition support, and tailored advice, positioning Acacia against competitors like Deloitte Labs by focusing on actionable insights rather than generic consulting (43:50).  \n- **Douglas Smith** highlighted the short average tenure of CIOs (~2 years), underscoring the need for rapid, thoughtful onboarding and decision-making support (44:41).\n\n## **AI and Data Strategy in Market Positioning**\n\nAI is positioned as an embedded capability within broader strategies, not as a standalone offering, reflecting varied client maturity and needs (15:36).  \n- **Douglas Smith** shared examples ranging from highly advanced pharma clients investing billions in AI with limited advisory opportunity but strong product potential, to manufacturers constrained by budgets and entrenched operations, indicating different engagement models (24:10).  \n- The middle market segment shows fragmented AI adoption with boards pressuring for clearer value and cohesion, providing a potential advisory entry point (27:34).  \n- Messaging will need to be segmented to resonate with CIOs focused on cost pressures and efficiency gains, recognizing that CIOs are often not the primary AI adoption leaders in their organizations (27:34).\n\n## **Content Creation and Marketing Collaboration**\n\nThe leadership team expressed strong willingness to engage in content creation, seeing it as a powerful tool to build credibility and connect with target audiences (45:05).  \n- **Douglas Smith** is actively using AI tools like Claude and ChatGPT to organize and repurpose thousands of documents into marketable frameworks and go-to-market materials (46:31).  \n- The team is open to experimenting with various content formats including video series, Loom videos, and conversational AI demos to tell stories and showcase expertise (48:21).  \n- This content-driven approach is expected to differentiate Acacia in a crowded market by highlighting authentic insights from practitioners rather than generic marketing messaging (49:26).\n\n## **Next Steps and Infrastructure Alignment**\n\nThe next meeting will focus on alignment and roadmap delivery after Acacia shares key documents and provides CRM access for data verification (57:06).  \n- The team uses **Pipedrive** for CRM management and will respond asynchronously to infrastructure and tool-related questions before the next call (58:12).  \n- Colin Costigan described their process of combining competitive research and internal data to build a detailed roadmap with annual goals and quarterly tasks, ensuring actionable marketing and sales alignment (56:50).  \n- The collaborative approach, with Acacia’s detailed input, is expected to accelerate lead generation and go-to-market effectiveness.","outline":null,"keywords":["Acacia","CIO transitions","Lead generation","AI readiness","Go-to-market strategy","Account-based marketing"],"overview":"- **Target Market Focus:** Prioritize organizations with $1-50 billion revenue; sectors include manufacturing, retail, and healthcare.  \n- **Lead Generation Gaps:** Currently manual signal capture; need automation to track leadership changes and market signals efficiently.  \n- **First Hundred Days Service:** Supports new leaders with fast, informed decisions; offers roadmap within 4-6 weeks using advanced tools.  \n- **AI Strategy Overview:** AI integrated into broader strategies; middle market faces varied adoption rates, needing tailored advisory approaches.  \n- **Content Creation Plans:** Team eager to leverage content for credibility; experimenting with diverse formats to share authentic insights.  \n- **Next Steps:** Upcoming meeting to align on roadmap after sharing key documents; focus on enhancing CRM data verification.","action_items":"\n**Douglas Smith**\nShare the pitch deck for Acacia, and the “First 100 Days” offering materials in markdown and slide formats (32:52)\nProvide the documented output of go-to-market conversations, including strategy, differentiation, offerings, and competitor analysis (51:17)\nShare access or links to the Manus knowledge base site with marketing and strategy frameworks (52:47)\n\n**Colin Costigan**\nFollow up by email requesting the above documents from Doug and include the whole team (58:47)\nSend marketing infrastructure questions to Kerry for asynchronous response (52:58)\nSchedule the next alignment meeting via availability link for Carrie to review calendars (58:20)\n\n**Kerry Marker**\nReview and respond to marketing infrastructure questions asynchronously (52:58)\nCoordinate calendar availability and confirm the next meeting date with Colin (58:21)\nPossibly assist in collating output from previous go-to-market discussions for sharing (51:42)\n\n**Justin Brown**\nEngage in creating marketing content and help coordinate conversation around content creation initiatives (45:05)\n"},"migrated_from":"contract_meetings","original_id":"af609c9e-867d-424d-95e8-63209f02725e","master_marketer":{"status":"migrated"}}'::jsonb,
