  '[{"text":"Provide any available carrier build plan numbers for the upcoming year to assist with forecasting and marketing strategy (46:47)","completed":false},{"text":"Share existing key contact and project data from Salesforce to support deeper pipeline analysis and marketing alignment (00:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Confirm internal preferences and realities around inquiry volume and process automation threshold (estimated 20/month) (53:41)","completed":false},{"text":"Collaborate with marketing team to specify marketing collateral needs (case studies, presentations, videos) to support new market entry (56:36)","completed":false},{"text":"Follow up with scheduling a roadmap presentation meeting, offering booking links and accommodating Friday preference (01:08:44)","completed":false},{"text":"Develop standard definitions for development stages (soft inquiry, inquiry, candidate, etc.) to align data tracking and reporting (27:02)","completed":false},{"text":"Prepare financial and marketing strategy roadmap based on client feedback for next meeting (00:00)","completed":false},{"text":"Lead creation of financial model and initial budget recommendations for marketing investment based on desired inquiry growth and realistic pilot scopes (8-10k suggested) (01:01:16)","completed":false},{"text":"Develop proposal for test campaigns balancing risk tolerance and expected outcomes, to build confidence and demonstrate value (01:03:48)","completed":false},{"text":"Provide input on internal budget comfort level and feasibility of marketing spend to guide strategy development (01:02:17)","completed":false},{"text":"Support discussion and modeling of automation needs triggered by inquiry volume growth (53:37)","completed":false},{"text":"Assist with detailed review and analysis of historic marketing agency work outcomes vs expectations (22:06)","completed":false}]'::jsonb,
